quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Kaaf, ndayidde Kur’ani eyekitiibwa (mazima ggwe Muhammad oli mubaka wa Katonda era olunaku lw’enkomerero lwa kubaawo)"
  50,2,Wabula bewunya okuba nti omutiisa (Nabbi Muhammad) yabajjira nga ava mu bo olwo nno abakaafiiri nebagamba nti kino kintu kya kitalo
  50,3,"(Nebagamba nti) abaffe bwetufa netufuuka ettaka (ate tuli bakuzzibwa!), bwekiba bwekityo okwo kudda okuli ewala ennyo"
  50,4,(Ekyo kibalemera bwereere okukkiriza anti) mazima tumanyi ekyo ettaka kye libakendezaako (nga lirya emibiri gyabwe) era tulina eggwanika erikuuma (buli kintu)
  50,5,"Wabula (tebakoma kwekyo era) baalimbisa amazima bwe gabajjira olwo nno bo baali mu mbeera ey’ekigambo ekitali kinywevu, (olumu bagamba bati olulala ne bagamba kirala)"
  50,6,Abaffe tebatunula ku ggulu waggulu waabwe (ne balaba) nga bwe twalizimba era netulinyiriza nga teririna bituli
  50,7,"Ne nsi twagiseeteeza era netugissaamu ensozi ennywevu, netumeza mu yo mu buli mutindo oguwa essanyu"
  50,8,Bibe ekizibula amaaso era ekyokubuulirira buli muddu adda eri Katonda
  50,9,"Era tussa amazzi okuva waggulu agoomukisa, olwo nno netumeza nago amalimiro n'empeke ebikungulwa"
  50,10,N’emitende emitumbiivu egirina ebirimba ebyeberese ku binnabyo
  50,11,"Nga byakulya bya baddu, era tulamusa nago (amazzi) ettaka effu eriba likaze, nabwekutyo okuzuukira bwe kuliba"
  50,12,"Oluberyeberye lwabwe (abantu be Makkah) abantu ba Nuhu baalimbisa, n’abantu ababbika Nabbi wabwe mu luzzi, n’abekika kya Thamud"
  50,13,Nabekika kya Aadi ne Firaawo ne baganda ba Luutu
  50,14,"N’abantu be nsi y’ebibira, n’abantu ba Tubbai, bonna baalimbisa ababaka, olwo nno nebikakata (ebibonerezo) byange bye nalagaanyisa"
  50,15,Abaffe twakoowa olwokutonda okwasooka (tube nga tweganya okubazzaawo)! nedda bo bali mu kutabulwa ku bikwata ku kutonda okupya
  50,16,Ng’ate ddala twatonda omuntu era tumanyi ekyo omwoyogwe kye gumulabankanya nakyo naye nga ffe tuli okumpi naye okusinga omusuwa (gwe) ogwobulamu
  50,17,"Mu kiseera we bamugyirako ebimukwatako (ba Malayika) abakwatibwako ensonga ababiri, nga bakikola ku mukono ogwa ddyo, n’ogwa kkono nga buli omu atudde ku ludda lwe"
  50,18,Olwo nno (omuntu) tayatula kigambo kyonna okugyako ng’aliko omulondoozi amubeerako buli kiseera
  50,19,Olwo nno obukambwe bwokufa nebujja mu mazima (nagambibwa nti) kino bulijjo kyobadde weewala
  50,20,Era engombe nefuuyibwa olwo lwe luliba olunaku olwalagaanyisibwa
  50,21,Buli muntu alijja nga aliko (Malayika) amugoba n’omujulizi
  50,22,"(Omukozi weebibi aligambwa nti) mazima wali mu bulagajjavu ku nsonga eno, kakano tukuggyeko ekibikka olwo nno eriiso lyo olwaleero lyogi nnyo"
  50,23,"Munne (Malayika eyamuberangako) aligamba nti, bino bye nnina ebimuwaako obujulizi binywevu nnyo"
  50,24,(Katonda aliragira Malayika alijja amugoba n'alimuwaako obujulizi nti) mukasuke mu muliro Jahannama buli mukafiiri omuwalaza we mpaka
  50,25,"Eyekiikanga mu kkubo lyo bulungi, eyabukanga ebikomo (bya mateeka ga Katonda) omubusabuusa"
  50,26,"Oyo eyassa ku Katonda ekisinzibwa ekirala, kale nno mumukasuke mu bibonerezo ebikambwe"
  50,27,"(Sitane) munywanyiwe aligamba nti, ayi Mukama omulabirizi waffe simubuzanga, wabula (ye yennyini) yali mu bubuze obwewala"
  50,28,(Katonda) aligamba nti temukayanira mu maaso gange nabawa dda okulabula (kwange nga mukyali ku nsi)
  50,29,Ekigambo tekikyusibwa gyendi (kasita mala okusalawo) era nze siyinza kuba mulyazamanyi eri abaddu
  50,30,"(Mutye) olunaku lwe tuligamba omuliro Jahannama nti abaffe ojjudde, negugamba nti abaffe waliyo enyongeza"
  50,31,"E jjana erisembezebwa eri abo abatya Katonda, nga tekyali wala"
  50,32,"Nebagambibwa nti, ekyo kye mwalaganyisibwa nga kya kufunwa oyo yenna eyadda ewa Katonda, n'akuma butiribiri (amateekage)"
  50,33,"(Yye yooyo) eyatya Katonda omusaasizi ennyo awamu nokuba nga tamulabako, era najja (olwaleero ku lunaku lw’enkomerero) n’omutima ogwemalira ku Katonda"
  50,34,"(Baligambibwa nti) mugiyingire (e jjana) mu mirembe, olwo lwe lunaku olulitandika obulamu obwolubeerera"
  50,35,"Balifuna byonna bye baagala nga bali mu yo (e jjana), era tulina ebyo kubongeza"
  50,36,"Era emirembe emeka gye twazikiriza oluberyeberye lwabwe (bano abakuwakanya ggwe Nabbi Muhammad), nga bo baali bamaanyi okubasinga, nebetoloola ensi (nga bakola buli kye bagala), abaffe waliwo obuwonero"
  50,37,Mazima mwekyo mulimu okubuulirira eri oyo alina omutima oba atega amatu era nga yenna waali (awuliriza)
  50,38,Era mazima twatonda eggulu omusanvu ne nsi neebiri wakati wa byombi mu nnaku mukaaga era tetwatukwako kukoowa kwonna
  50,39,"Kale gumikiriza ebyo bye bagamba, otendereze ebitendo bya Mukama omulabirizi wo nga enjuba tennavaayo, ne nga tennagwa"
  50,40,Era omutendereze ekiro nabuli luvannyuma lwa kuvunnama (okusaala e sswala ezalaalikibwa)
  50,41,Era wuliriza (ng’olinda) olunaku omukowooze lwalikowoola nga asinziira mu kifo kyo kumpi
  50,42,"Olunaku lwe bali wulira okubwatuka okwa mazima, olwo nno lwe luliba olunaku lwokufuluma (okuzuukira okuva mu ntaana)"
  50,43,"Mazima ffe, ffe tuwa obulamu era netutta, era gye tuli yokka yeeri obuddo"
  50,44,"Ku lunaku ettaka lweriyatika neribavaako (nga bazuukira) nebajja misinde (gye tuli), okwo kwe kukungaanya era kuliba kwangu ku ffe"
  50,45,"Ffe tusinga okumanya bye bagamba, era ggwe toli ku bo asobola kubawaliriza, n’olwekyo buulirira nga okozesa Kur’ani, oyo yenna atya ebitiisa byange"
  51,1,Ndayidde empewo ezifumuula enfuufu olufumuula
  51,2,Olwo nno nendayira ebire ebyetikka enkuba olwetikka
  51,3,N'amaato agaseeyeeya mu mazzi mu bwangu
  51,4,Era ndayidde Malayika ezigabanya Riziki okusinziira ku kiragiro ekiba kiziweereddwa
  51,5,Mazima bye mulaganyisibwa bya kutuukirira
  51,6,Era ddala olunaku lwo kusasula lwa kubaawo
  51,7,Ndayidde eggulu eryakolebwa mu ngeri ennungi
  51,8,Mazima mmwe muli mu kigambo ekyawukamu (temussa kimu ku bikwata ku Kur’ani)
  51,9,Awugulwa ku kyo oyo eyabuzibwa (natakkiriza)
  51,10,Baakolimirwa abo abalimba (aboogera ebitali bituufu ku Nabbi)
  51,11,Abo abali mu nnyanga ey’obukaafiiri nga babulubuuta
  51,12,Nga babuuza nti olunaku lwo kusasula luliba lwaddi
  51,13,Lwe lunaku bo lwe balyokebwa omuliro
  51,14,"(Nga bwe bagambibwa nti) mukombe ebibonerezo bya mmwe, kino kyekyo kye mwagambanga nti kibatuusibweko mu bwangu"
  51,15,Mazima abatya Katonda balibeera mu masamba nga mulimu n'ensulo za mazzi
  51,16,Nga beeyanza ebyo Mukama omulabirizi waabwe byalibawa (anti) mazima bo oluberyeberye lwekyo bali balongoosa
  51,17,Bebakanga e kiseera kitono mu kiro
  51,18,Ate nga mu ttumbi babanga mu kwe gayirira
  51,19,Era nga mu maali yaabwe mulimu omugabo gwo musabi nooyo atafuna kimumala (naye nga tasaba)
  51,20,"Era mu nsi mulimu obubonero (obulaga okubaayo kwa Katonda n’obuyinza bwe), eri abo abakkiriza obukkiriza obwa nnamaddala"
  51,21,Ne mu mmwe mwennyini (mulimu obubonero) abaffe temulaba
  51,22,Ne muggulu y'eri riziki za mmwe na byonna bye mulagaanyisibwa
  51,23,"Kale ndayidde Mukama omulabirizi we ggulu n'ensi, nti ekyo bwekityo bwekiri (era nga ekyo buli muntu yenna akimanyi) nga bwe mumanyi nti mwatula"
  51,24,Abaffe ebikwata ku bagenyi ba Ibrahim abekitiibwa bya kutuukako
  51,25,"Bwe baayingira weyali ne bagamba nti mirembe, (naye) naagamba nti mirembe (wabula muli) bantu abatamanyiddwa"
  51,26,Olwo nno nadda eri abantu be naleeta ennyana y'ente ensava (enjokye)
  51,27,Nagibasembereza naagamba nti abaffe nga temuulye
  51,28,"(Bwe bataalya) yawulira nga abatiddemu, ne bagamba nti totya era nebamuwa amawulire agessanyu ag'omwana omulenzi omumanyi ennyo"
  51,29,"(Awo wennyini) mukyala we naatuuka nga ayogerera waggulu nakuba ekyenyi kye, era naagamba nti (nze nga ndi) mukadde omugumba (nzaala ntya)"
  51,30,"(Ba Malayika) ne bagamba nti bwekityo Mukama omulabirizi wo bwagambye anti mazima yye bulijjo, ye mugoba nsonga omumanyi ennyo"
  51,31,"Ibrahim naagamba nti, ate mmwe ababaka nsonga ki ebaleese"
  51,32,Nebagamba nti mazima ffe tutumiddwa eri abantu abonoonyi
  51,33,Tube nga tubayiwako amayinja agomu bbumba ejjokye
  51,34,"Nga malambe okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wo, nga ga (kuzikiriza) abonoonyi abasukkiridde"
  51,35,(Katonda agamba) awo nno twagyamu oyo yenna eyakirimu (ekitundu ekyo) mu bakkiriza
  51,36,Naye tetwasangamu okugyako e nyumba emu eyabasiraamu
  51,37,Era twaleka mu kyo ekyo kuyiga eri abo abatya ebibonerezo ebiruma ennyo
  51,38,Era ne Musa (alimu ekyo kuyiga) bwe twamutuma ewa Firawo n’obujulizi obweyolefu
  51,39,Yagaana (okugoberera Musa) olwokwesigula abali emabega we era nagamba nti (Musa) mulogo oba mulalu
  51,40,Olwo nno netumukwatako ne ggye rye netubakasuka mu nnyanja nga naye anenyezebwa
  51,41,Ne mu Bantu ba Aadi (mulimu ekyokuyiga) bwe twabasindikira empewo engumba (etaliimu mukisa tereeta nkuba wadde okuwasisa ebibala)
  51,42,Nga tereka kintu kyonna kyeyitako okugyako nga ekifuula nga ensaano
  51,43,Ne mu bantu ba Thamud (mulimu ekyokuyiga) bwe bagambibwa nti mweyagale okumala akaseera katono
  51,44,"Wabula bo basukka ekiragiro kya Mukama omulabiririzi waabwe, olwo nno okubwatuka okwamaanyi ne kubatuukako nga nabo balaba"
  51,45,Tebaasobola kusituka (badduke) era tebaali ba kuwona
  51,46,N'abantu ba Nuhu nga bano tebannabaawo (nabo balimu ekyokuyiga anti nabo baazikirizibwa era nabo kya bagwanira) anti mazima bo baali bantu abonoonyi
  51,47,(N'ebirala ebirimu ekyokuyiga) ne ggulu twalizimba n'obuyinza (bwaffe) era mazima tukyaligaziya
  51,48,"N'ensi twagiseteeza, ddala nga ffe abatesiteesi abasinga"
  51,49,Era twatonda mu buli kintu emitindo ebiri ebiri (ekisajja ne kikazi) oba olyawo ne mujjukira
  51,50,Kale mudduke mudde eri Katonda mazima nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu gye muli okuva gyali
  51,51,"N’olwekyo temussanga ku Katonda ebisinzibwa ebirala, mazima nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu gye muli okuva gyali"
  51,52,Bwekityo abo ababakulembera tewali mubaka yabajjira okugyako nga bagamba nti mulogo oba mulalu
  51,53,Abaffe bakyeramira (nedda ssi bwekiri) wabula bo bantu be wagguzi
  51,54,Kale baveeko toli ggwe anenyezebwa
  51,55,Wabula bulirira anti mazima okubulirira kugasa abakkiriza
  51,56,Era ssaatonda amajinni n’abantu wabula lwakuba nti bansinze
  51,57,Sibaagalamu Riziki era ssaagala bandiise
  51,58,Mazima Katonda yye yaagaba Riziki nannyini maanyi omusobozi
  51,59,Mazima abo abeeyisa obubi balina ebyonoono nga ebyonoono bya bannaabwe n’olwekyo tebampapya (kubatuusaako bibonerezo mu bwangu)
  51,60,Okubonabona kuli eri abo abawakanya olunaku lwabwe olwo lwe baalaganyisibwa (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  52,1,Ndayidde olusozi (Sinaa)
  52,2,Ndayidde ekitabo ekiwandiike
  52,3,Mu mpapula ennyanjuluze
  52,4,Era ndayidde e nyumba etaggwako basinza (ba Malayika bagyetoloola olubeerera)
  52,5,Era ndayidde akasolya (k'eggulu) akasitufu
  52,6,Era ndayidde ennyanja ezijjudde amazzi
  52,7,Ddala ebibonerezo bya Mukama omulabirizi wo bya kutuukirira
  52,8,Tewali kigenda kubiremesa
  52,9,Ku lunaku eggulu lwe liri yuguuma oluyuguuma
  52,10,Ensozi nezitambula butambuzi
  52,11,N’olwekyo okubonabona ku lunaku olwo kuliba ku balimbisa
  52,12,Abo bo ababeera mu byolusaago nga bazannya
  52,13,"Ku lunaku lwe bali sindikirizibwa olusindikirizibwa, okuyingira omuliro Jahannama"
  52,14,Baligambibwa nti guno gwe muliro ogwo gwe mwali mulimbisa
  52,15,Abaffe lino ddogo oba mmwe temulaba
  52,16,"Mugwesogge, wabula ka mugumikirize oba temugumikiriza byonna kyekimu gye muli mazima ddala musasulwa ebyo bye mwali mukola"
  52,17,Mazima abatya Katonda baliba mu jjana n'ebyengera
  52,18,"Nga beyagala olwebyo Mukama omulabirizi waabwe byalibawa, era Mukama omulabirizi waabwe nabawonya ebibonerezo ebyomuliro Jahiimu"
  52,19,"(Abeeyisa obulungi baligambibwa nti) mulye era munywe, nga muyozayozebwa olwebyo bye mwakola"
  52,20,Baliba besigamye ku bitanda nga bisimbiddwa ennyiriri era tugenda ku bagatta na bakyala abo mu jjana
  52,21,"Abo abakkiriza, era ezzadde lyabwe neribagoberera mu bukkiriza, twakkiriza ezzadde lyabwe okubagoberera (baleme kufuna kiwubaalo obutaba nabo) era tetulikendeeza ku mirimu gyabwe kintu kyonna, era nga buli muntu (yye) gwe musingo gwebyo bye yakola"
  52,22,Era (nga ogyeko ebyogeddwa waggulu) tulibongeza ebibala n'ennyama ebyo bye baliyagala
  52,23,"(Nga bali mu jjana) baliyayaanira amagiraasi ge byo kunywa, naye nga ssi kujikubiramu lwogoolo wadde ebigambo ebikyafu"
  52,24,Era abalenzi abaliba balabika nga l'ulu akuumwa ennyo baliba babetoololamu nga babaweereza
  52,25,Era (abaliba mu jjana) abamu balyolekera bannabwe nga bewunaganya
  52,26,Nga bagamba nti mazima ffe mukusooka twabanga mu bantu baffe nga tutya (ebibonerezo bya Katonda)
  52,27,"Katonda natugonnomolako ekyengera, naatuwonya ebibonerezo byo muliro samuumu"
  52,28,"(Anti) mazima ffe okusooka twamusabanga (twamusinzanga), mazima yye yaayisa obulungi, omusaasizi ennyo"
  52,29,"Kale nno buulirira (ggwe Muhammad) anti ggwe olwe kyengera kya Mukama omulabirizi wo, toli mulaguzi wadde mulalu (nga abamu bwe babijweteka)"
  52,30,Oba bagamba nti (Muhammad) mutontomi gwetulekedde okukwata kwa walumbe
  52,31,"Bagambe nti mulindirire, anti mazima nze ndi wamu na mmwe mu balindirira"
  52,32,Abaffe amagezi gaabwe ge gabalagira kino oba bo bantu abaabula
  52,33,Oba bagamba nti (Muhammad) yajegunjirawo (Kur’ani ssi bwekiri) wabula tebakkiriza
  52,34,(Bwekiba nga yajigunjaawo) kale baleete ebigambo ebigifaanana bwebaba nga boogera mazima
  52,35,Oba batondwa awatali kintu (nti tewali Katonda yabatonda!) oba bo be batonda (ebitonde byonna nga nabo mwebali)
  52,36,"Oba be baatonda eggulu omusanvu ne nsi, nedda wabula bo tebakkiriza"
  52,37,"Oba be balina amawanika ga Mukama omulabirizi wo, oba bo be balina obuyinza (ku buli kintu)"
  52,38,Oba balina amadaala nga gebakozesa okuwuliriza ebifa waggulu (bwekiba bwekityo) kale abawuliriza baabwe baleete obujulizi obweyolefu
  52,39,Oba (Katonda) alina abaana ba buwala ate nga mmwe mulina abo bulenzi
  52,40,Oba obasaba musaala olwo nno bo nebaba nga bakaluubirirwa kusasula
  52,41,Oba balina okumanya ebyekusifu ne baba nga bo bawandiika (ebyekusifu bye bamanyi nebaba nga tebetaaga ggwe kubategeeza)
  52,42,Oba baagala kukola nkwe (bakulemese) wabula abo abakaafuwala be bakosebwa enkwe (ezo)
  52,43,"Oba balina ekisinzibwa ekitali Katonda (nga kye kibayinula), Katonda musukkulumu kwebyo bye bamugattako"
  52,44,Olw'obutakkiriza bwabwe ne bwe balaba ekibajjo nga kigwa okuva waggulu (kibazikirize) bandigambye nti bire ebyetuumye
  52,45,"Kale baleke okutuusa lwe balisisinkana olunaku lwabwe, olwo, ku lwo, lwe balizikirizibwa"
  52,46,"Olunaku enkwe zaabwe lwe zitalibagasa kintu kyonna, era nga bo tebalidduukirirwa"
  52,47,"Awamu n'ekyo mazima abo abeeyisa obubi batuusibwako ebibonerezo (ebirala kuno ku nsi) nga tebannatuuka ku biri, naye abasinga obungi ku bo tebamanyi"
  52,48,"Kale gumikiriza ku kusalawo kwa Mukama omulabirizi wo, anti mazima ggwe oli wansi wa kulabirira kwaffe. Era tendereza ebitendo bya Mukama omulabirizi wo, buli lwoliyimirira (okusaala)"
  52,49,Era n'ekiro mutendereze era omutendeze ekiseera we emmunyeenye wezibulira
  53,1,Ndayidde emunyeenye bweba nga egudde
  53,2,Munammwe (Muhammad) tabulanga kuva ku bulungamu era tayonoonanga
  53,3,Era tayogera nga asinziira ku kwagala (kwe)
  53,4,Tebiri byo (byayogera) okugyako okuba nti bubaka obuwereezebwa (gyali nga buva ewa Katonda)
  53,5,Yabimuyigiriza owamaanyi amayitirivu (Malayika Jiburilu)
  53,6,Nannyini busobozi eyeyoleka
  53,7,Bweyali mu bifo ebisinga okuba ebya waggulu mu bwengula
  53,8,Oluvanyuma (Jiburilu) yasembera olwo nebaba kumpi (ne Nabbi)
  53,9,Olwo nno (okusembera) nekuba nga okusemberagana kw'ensonda za kasale ebbiri oba kumpi okusingako awo
  53,10,Olwo nno (Katonda) naatumira omuddu we ekyo kye yamutumira nga akozesa Jiburilu
  53,11,Emmeme (ya Nabbi Muhammad) teyalimba kwebyo bye yalaba
  53,12,Abaffe mumuwakanya kwekyo kyalaba
  53,13,Ate nga mazima yamulaba omulundi omulala
  53,14,Mu kifo awali awali (omuti) Sidirat munitaha awakuumwa
  53,15,Weguli awo wewali e jjana ewummulirwamu (bo Malayika mwe bawummulira)
  53,16,Mu kiseera omuti Asidira bwe gwabikkibwa ekya gubikka
  53,17,Amaaso (ga Nabbi) tegawuguka wadde okusukka ekyo (kye yali ateekwa okulaba)
  53,18,Mazima yalaba mu bya magero ebya Mukama omulabirizi we ebinene
  53,19,Abaffe mulaba Latta ne Uzza
  53,20,Ne Mannaata ekibumbe ekirala ekyokusatu (bibumbe byali bisinzibwa nga Nabbi tannatumwa)
  53,21,Abaffe mmwe muzaala abalenzi yye nazaala bawala! (mwe bemutayagala newakubadde abalenzi na bawala ku Katonda kyekimu)
  53,22,Bwekiba bwekityo eyo ngabanya ejjudde kyekubiira
  53,23,"(Bye musinza) tebirina kyebiri okugyako okuba amannya gemwetuumira mmwe ne bakadde ba mmwe, Katonda tabissangako bujulizi bwonna (era ababisinza) tebalina kye bagoberera okugyako okuteebereza nokugoberera ebyo emyoyo gyabwe bye jaagala, so nga ate obulungamu bwabajjira nga buva ewa Mukama omulabirizi waabwe"
  53,24,Oba kiri nti omuntu asobola okufuna ekyo kye yeegomba (atuuke okwesalirawo okusinza ebibumbe ate naaba nga tavunaanwa)
  53,25,Wabula nno enkomerero ne ntandikwa bya Katonda yekka (n’olwekyo yekka yaasalawo)
  53,26,Era ba Malayika bameka abali mu ggulu omusanvu nga okuwolereza kwabwe tekugenda kugasa kintu kyonna okugyako oluvanyuma lwa Katonda okukkiriza gwaliba ayagadde era nasiima
  53,27,Mazima abo abatakkiriza nkomerero be bayita ba Malayika amannya ag’ekikazi
  53,28,"Era nga tebakirinaako kumanya kwonna, tebagoberera okugyako okuteebereza ate nga ddala okuteebereza tekulina kye kugasa awali amazima"
  53,29,"N’olwekyo va kwoyo ayawukana nokubulirira kwaffe, naatayagala okugyako obulamu bw'ensi"
  53,30,Ekyo kye kikomo kyabwe mu kumanya mazima Mukama omulabirizi wo yaasinga okumanya oyo abula naava ku kkubo lye era yaasinga okumanya oyo alungama
  53,31,Bya Katonda yekka ebyo ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu n'ebyo ebiri mu nsi (era yye ye nannyini mateeka kwe bikolera) olwo nno alisasula abo abayonoona olwebyo bye bakola era nga alisasula obulungi abo abalongoosa
  53,32,"Abo abeesamba ebyonoono ebinene ne byo buwemu okugyako ebitonotono, (anti) mazima Mukama omulabirizi wo mugazi wa kusonyiwa ye yaasinga okumanya ebikwata ku mmwe, okuva lwe yabatandikawo nga abagya mu ttaka ne mu kiseera we mwaberera mu mbuto za ba Maama ba mmwe, n’olwekyo temwetukuza anti yye yaasinga okumanya ani asinga okumutya"
  53,33,Abaffe olabye oyo akyuka (naava ku mazima)
  53,34,Era nawaayo katono bwamala ate nammira ddala
  53,35,"Abaffe (ekimukozesa ekyo) lwakuba nti alina okumanya ebyekusifu, olwo nno naaba nga abiraba"
  53,36,Oba tabuulirwanga ebyo ebiri mu bitabo bya Musa
  53,37,Ne Ibrahim oyo eyatuukiriza (bwe yalaganyisa Katonda)
  53,38,(Ebyo ebigamba nti) tewali mwoyo gulyetikka kibi kya mulala
  53,39,Era nti omunu tagenda kufuna okugyako ekyo kye yakolerera
  53,40,Era nti mazima okukola kwe kya ddaaki kulirabwa
  53,41,Oluvanyuma alikusasulwamu empeera esinga okuba enzijuvu
  53,42,Era nti mazima ewa Mukama omulabirizi wo yeeri enkomerero (ya buli kimu)
  53,43,Era nti mazima yye yaasesa era yaakaabya
  53,44,Era nti mazima yye yatta era yaawa obulamu
  53,45,Era nti mazima yatonda emitindo ebiri omusajja n'omukazi
  53,46,Abagya mu mazzi agazaala bwe gafulumizibwa (negateekebwa mu kifo ekituufu)
  53,47,Era nti mazima kuli ku ye yekka okusibusa okulala (okuzuukiza)
  53,48,Era nti mazima yye ya gaggawaza era naayavuwaza
  53,49,Era nti mazima yye ye Mukama omulabirizi we munyeenye eyitibwa Shiiraa (abakafiiri gye basinzanga)
  53,50,Era nti mazima yye yazikiriza abe kibiina kya A'adi abasooka
  53,51,Na be kibiina kya Thamud era nga teyalekawo (wadde omu)
  53,52,Na bantu ba Nuhu mu kusooka anti mazima bo be baali basinga okweyisa obubi n'okubula
  53,53,Era ye yae yazikiriza abantu ba be kitundu ekyavuunikibwa (Sodoma ne gomora)
  53,54,Olwo nno ne kikibuutikira ekya kibuutikira
  53,55,Kale olwo kiriwa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabiri wo kyobuusabuusa
  53,56,Ono (omubaka Muhammad) mutiisa ali mu luse lwa batiisa abaakulembera
  53,57,Enkomerero esembedde
  53,58,Tewali ayinza kugizzaayo bweriba ezze mpozzi Katonda
  53,59,Abaffe ebigambo bino bye mujereegerera
  53,60,Nemuba nga museka nemutakaaba
  53,61,Nga nammwe muzannya buzannyi
  53,62,Kale muvunname ku lwa Katonda era mumusinze (ekyo kye kisinga ebya mmwe bye mulimu)
  54,1,Enkomerero esembedde n'omwezi ne gubejjukamu
  54,2,Bwe balaba ekya magero bakyawukanamu ne bagamba nti lino ddogo eritakoma
  54,3,"Olwo nno ne balimbisa era ne bagoberera okwagala kwabwe, so nga buli kigambo kirina engeri gye kirina okubaamu (nungi oba mbi)"
  54,4,Ate nga ddala gaabatuukako amawulire ago agaalimu okukanga (okwandibamaze ne batya Katonda)
  54,5,"(Kur’ani eno) ejjudde amagezi etuukira ddala wala omuntu, (ekyekitalo) okutiisa kwokka tekumala (kwetagisaako okulungamya kwa Katonda)"
  54,6,Kale baveeko (olindirire) olunaku omukowooze lwalikowoola (abantu) kugenda eri ekintu ekitayagalwa
  54,7,"Amaaso gaabwe nga gatunudde wansi, baliva mu kabburi nga balinga ensenene ezisasaanye"
  54,8,"Balisaayirira okugenda eri omukowooze nga abakafiiri bwe bagamba nti, luno lunaku luzito"
  54,9,"Oluberyeberye lwabwe, abantu ba Nuhu balimbisa, olwo nno nebalimbisa omuddu waffe ne bagamba mbu muguwaddalu ate naatiisibwatiisibwa"
  54,10,Kyeyava asaba Mukama omulabirizi we nti mazima nze nemerdeddwa n’olwekyo nziruukirira
  54,11,Olwo nno netuggulawo emiryango gya waggulu ne tumuwa amazzi agafukumuka
  54,12,Era ettaka netulifukumulamu ensulo amazzi (ag’emirundi ebiri) ne gasisinkana okusinziira ku kiragiro ekyagerwa edda
  54,13,Netumusitulira na bonna abali naye mu lyato eryakolwa mu mbawo ne misumaali
  54,14,"Nga liddukira (ku mazzi ago) ku lwa buyinza bwaffe, ekyo nga kusasula eri oyo eyali awakanyizibwa"
  54,15,"Mazima (ekyafaayo ekyo) twakireka nga kya kuyiga, abaffe waliwo eyeebuliridde"
  54,16,(Nebalaba nti) ebibonerezo byange n’okutiisa byali bitya
  54,17,"Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu ebeere nga ebuulirira, abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,18,Abeekika kya Aadi baalimbisa naye ebibonerezo byange n’okutiisa byali bitya
  54,19,"Mazima ffe twabasindikira kikungunta omukambwe, mu lunaku olwe kikwa ekitaasalako olunaku lwonna"
  54,20,Eyasikulanga abantu (okuva ku ttaka) nga bagwa nga ebikonge by'emitende ebisiguddwa
  54,21,Naye ebibonerezo byange n’okutiisa byali bitya
  54,22,"Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu ebeere nga ebuulirira, abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,23,Abeekika kya Thamud baalimbisa okutiisa kwa (Nabbi waabwe Swaleh)
  54,24,"Olwo nno ne bagamba nti abaffe omuntu obuntu omu mu ffe, gwetuba tugoberera (netumala tukikola) olwo nno mazima ffe tujja kuba mu bubuze na bugwi bwa ddalu"
  54,25,Mu ffe fenna ye yaweereddwa obubaka! Nedda ssi bwekiri yye mulimba alina kyalubirira
  54,26,Enkya bajja kumanya ani mulimba omwerazi
  54,27,"(Anti) mazima ffe tujja kuweereza engamiya nga kikemo gye bali, olwo nno batunuulire nkaliriza era ogumikirize (ku nneeyisa yaabwe embi)"
  54,28,"Era bategeeze nti (okuva engamiya lwezze) ddala amazzi ga kugabanyizibwa wakati waabwe nayo, nga buli luwalo lutuukirizibwa, (nyinirwo yaalina okufuna amazzi keebe ngamiya oba bantu)"
  54,29,Olwo nno baakowoola mu nnaabwe neyeesowolayo naafumita (engamiya)
  54,30,Naye ebibonerezo byange n’okutiisa byali bitya
  54,31,"(Anti) mazima twabasindikira olubwatuka lumu, olwo nno ne baba nga ebisubi ebigwa okuva ku lugo (lwo muntu agenderera okukuuma ebisolo bye)"
  54,32,"Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu, ebeere nga ebuulirira abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,33,Abantu ba Luutu baalimbisa obubaka
  54,34,"Mazima ffe twabasindikira kibuyaga owa mayinja (eyabasanyaawo bonna) okugyako abantu b’o mu maka ga Luutu, twabawonya mu ttumbi"
  54,35,"Ekyo kyengera okuva gye tuli bwe tutyo nno, bwe tusasula oyo eyeebaza"
  54,36,Mazima (Luutu) yabeekesa okukwata kwaffe wabula nebabuusabuusa okulabula (kwe)
  54,37,"Mazima baagezaako okumusendasenda abawe abagenyi be (babasiyage) olwo nno netuziba amaaso gaabwe, ne bakomba ku bibonerezo byange n'okulabula kwange"
  54,38,Era mazima ebibonerezo ebitasalako bya bazinda mu matulutulu
  54,39,Olwo nno nebakomba ku bibonerezo byange n’okulabula kwange
  54,40,Mazima Kur’ani twagifuula nyangu ebeere nga ebuuririra abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde
  54,41,Mazima okulabula kwajjira abantu ba Firawo
  54,42,"Baalimbisa ebigambo byaffe byonna, olwo nno netubakwata enkwata ya Nantakubwa ku mukono, nannyini buyinza"
  54,43,Abakafiiri ba mmwe be balungi okusinga abo! oba (ekibayinula) mulina akalagaane ku butavunaanwa nga kawandiikibwa mu bitabo ebitukuvu ebyasooka
  54,44,Oba (ekibayinula lwakuba) bagamba nti ffe tuli bangi nga twegasse tusobola okwetaasa
  54,45,(Zibasanze) ekibiina (ekyo) kijja kuwangulwa era bakubeyo amabega (badduke)
  54,46,(Byonna bye baliko temuli) wabula olunaku lw’enkomerero ye ndagaano yaabwe era olunaku lw’enkomerero lwelusinga obukalubo n’obukaawu
  54,47,Mazima abonoonyi bali mu bubuze na bugwi bwa ddalu
  54,48,(Bandibadde bajjukira) olunaku lwe baliwalulwa ku byenyi byabwe mu muliro (nga bwe bagambibwa nti) mukombe ku bulumi bw’omuliro Sakara
  54,49,Mazima ffe buli kintu twakitonda mu ngeri nga bwe kisaana okuba
  54,50,(Ate mu kukola ebintu byonna) ekiragiro kyaffe tekiri okugyako kimu nga kiringa lutemya lwa liiso
  54,51,"Era ddala twazikiriza abafaanana nga mmwe, abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,52,Na buli kintu kyonna kye baakola kiri mu kitabo
  54,53,Era buli kitono n'ekinene kyawandiikibwa
  54,54,Mazima abatya Katonda balibeera mu jjana n’emigga (egiriba gikulukutira wansi waazo)
  54,55,Mu kifo ekya mazima ew’omufuzi nannyini buyinza
  55,1,(Katonda) omusaasizi ennyo
  55,2,Yayigiriza (omuntu) Kur’ani
  55,3,Yatonda omuntu
  55,4,Yamuyizigiriza okunnyonnyola
  55,5,Enjuba n’omwezi bitambulira ku nteekateeka (eyabiweebwa)
  55,6,Ebiddo n’emiti (bivunnama nga bisinza Katonda)
  55,7,Era eggulu yalisitula era nassaawo obwenkanya
  55,8,Mube nga temusukka ebipimo (mu kutuukiriza obwenkanya)
  55,9,Era muyirizeewo ebipimo mu bwenkanya era temukendezanga minzane
  55,10,N'ensi yagiteerawo ebitonde
  55,11,Nga erimu ebibalo n’emitende egirina ebirimba
  55,12,N'ebimera ebye mpeke eziri mu bikuta n’ebimera ebya kawoowo
  55,13,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,14,Yatonda omuntu mu bumba eggumu eriringa ejjokye
  55,15,Ate naatonda amajinni mu bitawuliro by’omuliro
  55,16,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,17,"Mukama omulabirizi w’o buvanjuba bwombi, era Mukama omulabirizi w'obugwanjuba bwombi"
  55,18,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,19,Yagatta enyanja ebbiri (ez’amazzi agenjawulo aganyweka na gatanyweka) zesisinkana
  55,20,"Wakati wa zombi waliwo ekyawula, tezigenda kwetabula"
  55,21,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,22,Ate nga mu zombi mwe muva Luulu ne Marijaani (amayinja ag’omuwendo)
  55,23,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,24,Era gatambula ku lwo buyinza bwe amaato agakolwa ku lwo kutambulira ku nyanja nga galinga ensozi
  55,25,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,26,Buli kyonna ekigiriko (ensi) kya kuggwawo
  55,27,"Olwo nno wasigalewo obwennyini bwa Mukama omulabirizi wo, nannyini kugulumizibwa era nannyini kitiibwa"
  55,28,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,29,Bimusaba ebyo ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu n'ensi (naye nga) buli lunaku aba ku ngeri ndala (mu kugera kwe)
  55,30,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,31,"Tujja kubateerawo ekiseera abange mmwe ebitonde ebizito ebibiri (amajinni n’abantu, ekiseera ekyo mwe tulibalira buli omu)"
  55,32,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,33,"Abange mmwe ab'oluse lwa majinni n’oluse lwa bantu, bwe muba musobola okuyita mu bitundu bye ggulu omusanvu n'ensi (mube nga mudduka ku Katonda) kale muyitemu (naye) temuyinza kuyitamu okugyako nga mulina obusobozi"
  55,34,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,35,"Musindikirwa mwe ab'emirundi ebiri (amajinni n’abantu) ebitawuliro byomuliro, n’ekikomo ekisaanuuse (naye temusobola kwetaasa)"
  55,36,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,37,Olwo nno eggulu bwe liribajjuka nerirabika nga ekimuli ekimyufu (olwamaanyi g’omuliro) neriba nga omuzigo omusanuuse
  55,38,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,39,Ku lunaku olwo ekibi omuntu (kye yakola) tekigenda kubuuzibwa muntu mulala oba ejinni
  55,40,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,41,"Abonoonyi balimanyibwa olwobubonero bwabwe, olwo nno nebakwatibwa ku nviiri z’o mu buwompo n’ebigere (nebamenyebwamu nebakasukwa mu muliro)"
  55,42,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,43,Baligamba nti guno gwe muliro Jahannama abonoonyi gwe baali balimbisa
  55,44,Bagenda kwetoloolera wakati waagwo ne wakati w'olwegye oluyitirivu lwokwokya
  55,45,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,46,Era oyo eyatya okuyimirira mu kifo kya Mukama omulabirizi we alina e jjana bbiri
  55,47,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,48,Ezirimu amatabi agalanda
  55,49,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,50,Mu zombi (e jjana) mulimu ensulo bbiri ezikulukuta
  55,51,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,52,Mu zombi mulimu ku buli kika kya kibala emitindo ebiri ebiri
  55,53,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,54,"(Abalibeeramu) baliba bagalamidde ku byaliiro, nga munda mwabyo mulimu Liiri omuzito, nga ne nimiro za jjana zombi ebibala byamwo bireebeeta (byangu bya kulaba era byangu bya kunoga)"
  55,55,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,56,Mu zo (e jjana) mulimu abakyala abamaaso amakkakkamu (embeerera) nga tebakwatwangako muntu yenna wadde ejinni oluberyeberye lwabwe (abo abaliba babaweereddwa mu jjana)
  55,57,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,58,(Olwo bulungi bwabwe) baliba nga Yaakut ne Marijaan (amayinja ag’omuwendo)
  55,59,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,60,Abaffe empera y’okukola obulungi (eyinza okuba ekintu ekirala kyonna) okugyako okusasulwa obulungi
  55,61,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,62,Nga oggyeko ezo ebbiri baakufuna ate e jjana endala bbiri
  55,63,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,64,Eza kiragala omukwafu
  55,65,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,66,Mu zombi mulimu ensulo bbiri ezifukumuka amazzi
  55,67,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,68,Mu zombi mulimu ebibala n’emitende ne nkoma mawanga
  55,69,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,70,Muzonna awamu zirimu abakyala abalungi be mpisa era abalungi mu ndabika
  55,71,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,72,Ba nalulungi abatafulumafuluma mu weema
  55,73,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,74,"Nga tebakwatwangako muntu yenna wadde ejinni oluberyeberye lwabwe, (abo abaliba babaweereddwa mu jjana)"
  55,75,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,76,Baliba besigamye ku mitto egiriko ebibikka ebya kiragala ne byaliiro ebirungi ennyo
  55,77,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,78,Sukkulumu erinnya lya Mukama omulabirizi wo nannyini kugulumizibwa n’okuweebwa ekitiibwa
  56,1,Ekiseera ekitaliimu kubuusabuusa bwe kirituuka
  56,2,Okutuuka kwakyo tekuliimu kubuusabuusa
  56,3,Kirikakkanya (abeeyisa obubi era) kirisitula (abeeyisa obulungi)
  56,4,Ensi bwe rikankanyizibwa olukankana
  56,5,N'ensozi nezimerengulwa olumerengulwa
  56,6,Olwo nno nezifuuka enfuufu efumuuka
  56,7,Era mmwe nemuba emitendera esatu
  56,8,"Olwo nno newabaawo ogwa ba nannyini mukono ogwa ddyo, yye omanyi okubeera ku mukono ogwaddyo kye kitegeeza"
  56,9,"Era newabaawo n’ogwa ba nannyini mukono ogwa kkono, yye omanyi okubeera ku mukono ogwa kkono kye kitegeeza"
  56,10,"Newabaawo n’ogwabo abaakulembera, abalikulembera mu buli kimu"
  56,11,Abo be bo kusembezebwa (ewa Katonda)
  56,12,Nga bali mu jjana ez'ebyengera
  56,13,Bangi mu bibiina ebyasooka
  56,14,Nabatono mu kibiina kya bantu abenkomerero (abekibiina kya Nabbi Muhammad)
  56,15,(Balibeera) ku bitanda ebyakolebwa mu zzaabu n'amayinja amalala agomuwendo
  56,16,Baliba bagalamidde ku byo nga boolekaganye (nga banyumya)
  56,17,"Abaweereza abalenzi, abolubeerera baliba babayitamu"
  56,18,"Nga balina ebikopo, amabinika ne giraasi ebijjudde omubisi oguva mu nsulo"
  56,19,Tebagenda kulumwa mutwe olwagwo era tebagenda kutamiira
  56,20,N’ebibala (ebye njawulo) mwebyo bye baliba nga basazeewo
  56,21,Ne nnyama y’ebinyonyi eyo gye baliyagala
  56,22,N'abakyala abalungi abamaaso agatemagana
  56,23,Nga balinga Luulu akuumibwa obutiribiri
  56,24,(Ebyo byonna) nga mpeera yeebyo bye baali bakola (ebirungi ku nsi)
  56,25,Tebagenda kuwulira mu yo luyogaano wadde ebigambo ebyesittaza
  56,26,"Okugyako okugamba nti mirembe, mirembe"
  56,27,"Abantu bo ku mukono ogwa ddyo, abaffe omanyi abantu bo ku mukono ogwa ddyo baliba batya"
  56,28,Balituula (mu bittuluze) by'emiti gya Sidiri atemeddwako amaggwa
  56,29,N'ensuku ezirimu amatooke agaliko ebiwagu ebiberekaganye
  56,30,N'ebisikirize ebigazi
  56,31,N'amazzi agakulukuta awatali kusalako
  56,32,N'ebibala ebingi
  56,33,Ebitaggwawo ate ebitatekebwako kkomo
  56,34,N'ebyaliiro ebisuffu ebya waggulu
  56,35,Mazima ffe twatonda abakyala bo mu jjana olutonda
  56,36,Olwo nno twabatonda nga mbeerera
  56,37,Nga bulijjo baganzi eri ba bbaabwe nga tebakakiddwa
  56,38,Nga bo ba bantu abalibeera ku mukono ogwa ddyo
  56,39,Bangi mu bibiina ebyasooka
  56,40,Era bangi mu kibiina kya bantu ab'enkomerero (ab’ekibiina kya Nabbi Muhammad)
  56,41,"Ate abantu bo ku mukono ogwa kkono, abaffe omanyi abantu bo ku mukono ogwa kkono baliba batya"
  56,42,Balibeera mu kibuyaga ayokya n’amazzi ageeseze
  56,43,"Nga nebisikirize mwe balyewogoma, biriba bya mu mukka omuddugavu ogwokya"
  56,44,Biriba tebinnyogoga era nga tebisanyusa
  56,45,Anti mazima bo oluberyeberye lwa kino baali baamalibwawo ebyo kwe jalabya
  56,46,Era baalemeranga ku kibi ekinene (bwe baalayiranga nti tewali kuzuukira)
  56,47,"Era baagamba nga nti bwetufa netufuuka ettaka, era netusigala ngumba gumba abaffe tulizuukizibwa"
  56,48,Ne bakadde baffe abasooka (nabo bwe batyo)
  56,49,Bagambe ggwe (Nabbi Muhammad) nti mazima abasooka n'aboluvanyuma
  56,50,Ddala ba kukunganyizibwa ku lunaku olwasalibwawo olumanyiddwa
  56,51,"Oluvanyuma mazima mmwe, abange mmwe ababuze abalimbisa"
  56,52,Ddala mugenda kulya ku muti gwa zakkumu
  56,53,Nulijjuza nagwo embuto (gujjuze embuto zammwe)
  56,54,Olwo nno munywereko amazzi ageeseze
  56,55,Mugenda kunywa ng'ennywa ye ngamiya erina ennyonta
  56,56,Obwo bwe buliba obugenyi bwabwe ku lunaku lwo kusasula
  56,57,"Ffe twabatonda, kale singa mukkiriza (okusinziira kwekyo)"
  56,58,Abaffe mulaba amazzi (agazaala) ge muteeka mu nnabaana
  56,59,Abaffe mmwe mugatonda oba ffe batonzi
  56,60,"Ffe twagera netussa wakati wa mmwe okufa, (netubakakasaako okufa) era tetuli ffe ba kulemesebwa"
  56,61,"Okuba nga tuwaanyisa abalinga mmwe (mu mmwe) olwo nno mmwe, netubakolamu ebirala bye mutamanyi"
  56,62,Ate nga ddala mwamanya entandikwa eyasooka (engeri Katonda gye yabatondamu) kale singa mwebulirira
  56,63,Abaffe mulaba ebyo bye mulima
  56,64,Abaffe mmwe mubimeza oba ffe tumeza
  56,65,Singa twagadde tusobola okubifuula ebikaze nemusigala nga mwewunaganya
  56,66,(Nga mugamba nti) mazima ffe tetufunye ate nga tubanjibwa
  56,67,(Si kye kyokka) wabula ffe tummiddwa
  56,68,Abaffe mulaba amazzi ago gemunywa
  56,69,Mwe mugassa okuva mu bire oba ffe tugassa
  56,70,Singa twagadde twaligafudde olukalabule kale singa mwebaza (Katonda olwo kugafuula amalungi)
  56,71,Abaffe mulaba omuliro ogwo gwe mukuma
  56,72,"Abaffe mmwe mwatandikawo omuti gwagwo, oba ffe twagutandika"
  56,73,"Ffe twagufuula kya kujjukiza, era nga gwa mugaso eri abatambuze (abataba na byoto bibakumira muliro)"
  56,74,Kale tendereza erinnya lya Mukama omulabirizi wo owekitiibwa
  56,75,Tewali kingaana kulayira bifo bya munyeenye
  56,76,Era mazima kwo ddala kulayira kunene singa mubadde mumanyi
  56,77,Okuba nti ddala yo Kur’ani yakitiibwa
  56,78,Eri mu kitabo ekikuumibwa obutiribiri (ku Lawuhu al mahfudhu)
  56,79,Takikwatako okugyako abaatukuzibwa (ba malayika abatalina bukyafu bwa mibiri oba obwe nzikiriza)
  56,80,Essibwa okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi w’ebitonde
  56,81,Abaffe ebigambo bino (ebya Kur’ani) mmwe bye mugayaalirira
  56,82,Okugirimbisa mmwe ne mukifuula okuba nga ye Riziki yammwe
  56,83,Singa omwoyo wegutuukira mu ddokooli (musala amagezi nemugutaasa)
  56,84,Ate nga mmwe mu kiseera ekyo mubaawo nga mutunula
  56,85,"Era ffe tuba okumpi naye okusinga mmwe, naye temulaba"
  56,86,Kale singa mwali temufugibwa (Katonda)
  56,87,"Muyinza okugamba nti mwandiguzizzaamu mu mubiri, bwe muba mwogera mazima"
  56,88,Naye (omufu) bwaba mu bo kumpi (ne Katonda)
  56,89,Aliba mu kwesiima na mirembe na jjana eye byengera
  56,90,Ate bwaba mu bantu bo ku mukono ogwa ddyo
  56,91,"(Aliyozebwayozebwa nti) emirembe gibeere ku ggwe, olwokuba oli mu bantu bo ku mukono ogwa ddyo"
  56,92,Wabula bwabeera nga ali mu balimbisa ababuze
  56,93,(Oyo nno) obugenyi (bwe) bwalwegye lwa mazzi
  56,94,Nakwesogga muliro Jahiimu
  56,95,Mazima ebyo ge mazima agannamaddala
  56,96,Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama omulabirizi wo owekitiibwa
  57,1,"Byonna ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu ne nsi bitendereza Katonda, era yye ye nnantakubwa ku mukono mugoba nsonga"
  57,2,"Bubwe yekka obufuzi bwe ggulu omusanvu n'ensi,awa obulamu era natta, era yemuyinza ku buli kintu"
  57,3,"Yye ye yasooka era ow'enkomerero, era yye yaali waggulu wa buli kintu, era yaasooka wansi, nga wansii we tewali kintu kirala, era yye amanyi ebifa ku buli kintu"
  57,4,"Yye yooyo eyatonda eggulu omusanvu n'ensi mu nnaku omukaaga, oluvanyuma yatebenkera ku Arish, amanyi ebikka ku nsi nebigifuluma n'ebyo ebikka okuva mu ggulu nebiryambukamu, era yye aba wamu na mmwe wonna wemuba, era Katonda alabira ddala ebyo bye mukola"
  57,5,Bubwe yekka obufuzi bwe ggulu omusanvu n'ensi era eri Katonda ebintu byonna gye bizzibwa
  57,6,"Abuliza ekiro mu musana, era naabuliza omusana mu kiro, era yye amanyidde ddala ebiri mu bifuba"
  57,7,"Mukkirize Katonda n’omubaka we, era mugabe kwebyo bya yabafuula abasigire mu byo, abo nno abakkiriza mu mmwe era ne bagaba, balina empeera ensuffu"
  57,8,"Mwabaaki obutakkiriza Katonda ng’ate omubaka abakowoola mube nga mukkiriza Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, ate nga yabakozesa endagaano (kwekyo), bwe muba abakkiriza (nga mukyali ku ndagaano gyeyabakozesa)"
  57,9,"Yye yooyo assa ku mudduwe (Muhammad) ebigambo ebinnyonnyofu, abe nga abagya mu bizikiza mudde eri ekitangaala, era mazima Katonda mukwata mpola ku mmwe, musaasizi nnyo"
  57,10,"Mutya bwe mutayinza kuwaayo mu kkubo lya Katonda ng’ate obusika bwe ggulu omusanvu n'ensi bwa Katonda, oyo eyawaayo mu mmwe nga obuwanguzi (bwe Makkah) tebunnabaawo, era nalwana (tayinza) kwenkana ne yakikola oluvanyuma) bali (abasoose) be be ddaala erya waggulu okusingaabo abaawaayo oluvanyuma era ne balwana. Naye nga bonna Katonda yabalagaanyisa (okubasasula) ebirungi, Katonda amanyidde ddala ebyo bye mukola"
  57,11,"Ani oyo awola Katonda oluwola olulungi, olwo nno alumubalizeemu, era nga alina empeera eweesa ekitiibwa"
  57,12,"Olunaku lwoliraba abakkiriza abasajja n'abakkiriza abakazi, nga ekitangaala kyabwe kibali mu maaso gaabwe, ne ku mikono gyabwe egya ddyo nga ba Malayika babagamba nti ekyessanyu kya mmwe olwaleero ze jjana nga gikulukutira wansi waazo emigg, muli ba kuzibeeramu obugenderevu, ekyo kyo kwe kwesiima okusukkulumu"
  57,13,"(Fumitiriza) olunaku abananfusi abasajja na bannanfusi abakazi lwe baligamba abo abakkiriza, nti mutulinde tulabise ku kitangaala kya mmwe, walirangirirwa nti mudde emabega wa mmwe (gye muvudde) munoonye ekitangaala, olwo nno waliteekwa wakati waabwe ekikomera nga kiriko omulyango, nga munda waakyo (ku ludda eribeera abakkiriza) waliyo okusaasira, ate nga ebweru waakyo (ku ludda eribeera abananfusi) ebibonerezo gyebiriba bisibuka"
  57,14,"Balibakowoola (nga bagamba nti mutumma ekitangaala) abaffe tetwali na mmwe, baligamba nti wewaawo, naye mazima mmwe, mwesuula mu bikemo, ne mulindiriza, ne mubuusabuusa ,essuubi ekyavaamu neribagayaaza okutuusa ekigambo kya Katonda lwekyajja era ebigayaaza nebibajja ku Katonda"
  57,15,"Kale nno olwaleero temuli ba kuggibwako nunuzi, wadde okugiggya kwabo abakaafuwala (mwenna) obuddo bwa mmwe muliro, ggwo gwe gubagyamu, naye nga buddo bubi"
  57,16,"Abaffe ekiseera tekituuse eri abo abakkiriza okuba nga emitima gyabwe gigonda ku lwokwogera ku Katonda, ne ku lwebyo ebyamazima ebisse, baleme kuba nga abo abaweebwa ekitabo (Tauraati ne Injili) oluberyeberye, olwo nno ekiseera ekyayitawo ku bo (wakati waabwe ne ba Nabbi) nekiwanvuwa, emitima gyabwe negikakanyala, era bangi mu bo bonoonyi"
  57,17,"Mumanye nti mazima Katonda awa obulamu ettaka oluvanyuma lwokufa (okukala) kwalyo, mazima tubannyonnyodde ebigambo (byaffe) mube nga mutegeera"
  57,18,"Mazima abasajja abasaddaaka, na bakyala abasaddaaka, era ne bawola Katonda oluwola olulungi, (bye bawaayo) Katonda abibakubisizaamu, era balina empeera eyekitiibwa"
  57,19,"Era abo abakkiriza Katonda n'ababaka be, abo bbo be bakkiriza abannamaddala, na balafuubana mu kuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda, balina empeera yaabwe n'ekitangaala kyabwe ewa Mukama omulabirizi waabwe, ate abo abakafuwala ne balimbisa ebigambo byaffe, abo be ba nannyini muliro"
  57,20,"Mumanye nti mazima obulamu bwensi muzannyo na binyumo, nakwewunda nakwewaana wakati wa mmwe, nakulaga bungi bwa mmaali na baana, (wabula ebyo tebisaana kubuza muntu) anti bifaananako enkuba (emeza ebirime) ebimera byabyo nebisanyusa abalimi, oluvanyuma nebikula, olwo nno noobiraba nga byengedde, oluvanyuma nebifuuka ebisusunku naye mu bulamu obwenkomerero waliyo ebibonerezo ebikakali. (nga era bwe waliyo) ekisonyiwo n’okusiima ebiva ewa Katonda. Obulamu bwensi tebulina kye buli okugyako okuba okweyagala okugayaaza obugayaaza"
  57,21,"Muvuganye nga mudda eri ekisonyiwo ekiva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (era nga mudda), eri e jjana obugazi bwayo bwenkana obugazi bwe ggulu ne nsi nga yategekerwa abo abakkiriza Katonda nababaka be. Ebyo bigabwa bya Katonda, abiwa oyo gwaba ayagadde, era Katonda ye nnyini bigabwa ebisuffu"
  57,22,"Tewali kabi kabaawo mu nsi, wadde okutuuka ku mmwe okugyako nga kaali mu kitabo nga tetunnaba ku katuusaawo, ddala ekyo kyangu nnyo ku Katonda"
  57,23,"Muleme kukubandeka mwoyo kwekyo ekiba kibasubye, era muleme kusanyuukirira olwekyo kyaba abawadde, Katonda bulijjo tayagala mwerazi omwewulize"
  57,24,"(Abantu abo) beebo abakodowala ne bakalaatira n’abantu obukodo, oyo yenna akyuka (naava ku biragiro bya Katonda) mazima Katonda yye yaatali mwetaavu, atenderezebwa"
  57,25,"Ddala twatuma ababaka baffe nga baleeta obunnyonnyofu netubassaako ekitabo (nga kirimu amateeka) era netubalagira okukozesa Minzaani, abantu babe nga bayimirizaawo obwenkanya, era netussa (wo) ekyuma nga kirimu amaanyi amasuffu n’emigaso (nfaafa) eri abantu, olwo nno Katonda alyoke amanye oyo amutaasa era nataasa ababaka be, awamu n’okuba nti (Katonda) talabwa. Mazima Katonda wa maanyi, nantakubwa ku mukono"
  57,26,"Mazima twatuma Nuhu ne Ibrahim netussa muzadde lyabwe bombi obwa Nabbi n’ekitabo, olwo nno mu bo mulimu omulungamu naye abasinga obungi mu bo bonoonyi"
  57,27,"Oluvanyuma twagobereza ku buufu bwabwe ba Nabbi baffe, kwabo twagoberezaako Isa mutabani wa Mariam, netumuwa ne Injil, era twassa mu mitima gyabo abamugoberera okulumiriganwa n'okusaasira, era bakolera ku bu sosodooti bwe baagunjaawo, tetububawandiikangako (wabula bo bwegunjirawo) mbu nga banoonya okusiima kwa Katonda, olwo nno ate tebabukolerako nga bwekyali kyetaagisa okubukolerako, kale netuwa abo abakkiriza mu bo empeera yaabwe, era abasinga obungi mu bo bonoonyi"
  57,28,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza mutye Katonda era mukkirize n’omubaka we, ajja kubawa okusaasira kwe emirundi ebiri, era abateerewo ekitangaala nga kwe mutambulira, era abasonyiwe, bulijjo Katonda musonyiyi nnyo, musaasizi"
  57,29,"(Ebyo byonna lwakuba nti) abaweebwa ekitabo babe nga bamanya nti tebalina kintu kyonna ku bigabwa bya Katonda kye balinako buyinza, era bamanye nti ebigabwa byonna biri mu mukono gwa Katonda, abiwa gwaba ayagadde, bulijjo Katonda ye nanyini bigabwa ebisuffu"
  58,1,Ddala Katonda awulidde ebigambo byo mukyala ey'emulugunyizza gyoli ku bba era n'awaaba eri Katonda era Katonda abadde awulira ebigambo bye mubadde muwanyisiganya anti Katonda bulijjo awulira era alaba
  58,2,Abo bonna mu mmwe abagamba bakyala baabwe nti emigongo gyabwe giringa egya ba nnyabwe (abo be bakigamba) tebabangako ba maama baabwe. Ba maama baabwe beebo ababazaala. (mu kwogera batyo) mazima bbo boogera ekigambo ekibi. Mu kiseera kye kimu nga kigunje. Wabula mazima ddala Katonda alekera era asonyiwa
  58,3,"Abo bonna abazira bakazi baabwe olw'okulayira nti kubo balinga bannyaabwe ate oluvanyuma nebaddayo eri ekyo kye baali balayiridde (oyo akikola) ateekwa okuta omuddu nga tannaba kuddayo kulabagana namukyalawe. Ekyo nno kyemuteekwa okukola, anti Katonda amanyi nnyo byonna byemukola"
  58,4,"Oyo aba tasobodde kuta muddu nga tannalabagana na mukyalawe ateekwa okusiiba emyezi ebiri nga gigoberegana, wabula oyo aba tasobodde ateekwa okuliisa ba masikiini nkaaga. Ekyo kibafuule abakkiriza Katonda n'omubakawe, ago mateeka g'aKatonda era bulijjo abawakanya amateeka g'a Katonda bagenda kutuukibwako ebibonerezo ebiruma"
  58,5,"Mazima abo abawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe baswavu nga abaabasooka bwe baaswazibwa, ate nga twassa amateeka agannyonnyola (Haraamu ne Halaal) naye abo abagawakanya bajja kutuukibwako ebibonerezo ebigenda okubanyoomesa"
  58,6,"Olunaku Katonda lwalibazuukiza bonna n'ababuulira ebyo byebaakola, Katonda yabikunganya n'abikomekkereza. So ng'ate bbo baabyerabira. Bulijjo Katonda mujulizi ku buli kintu"
  58,7,"Abaffe tomanyi nti mazima Katonda amanyi ebyo ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu n'ebyo ebiri mu nsi, nga tewali kafubo konna kakabe k'abasatu okugyako nga yye waakuna, wadde ak'abataano okugyako nga yye w'amukaaga wadde abatono abatenkana basatu oba abali waggulu w'omukaaga okugyako Katonda aba nabo awo wonna webali, oluvanyuma Katonda ku lunaku lw’enkomerero agenda kubategeeza ebyo byonna byebaali bakola. Anti Katonda amanyi buli kintu kyonna"
  58,8,"Abaffe tolaba abo abagaanibwa okukola obufubo (obwenkwe) oluvanyuma ne baddamu ekyo kyenyini ekyabagaanibwa, nga bogeraganya wakati waabwe mu nkukutu olw'okukola ebikyamu n'obulabe n'okujeemera omubaka. Era nga bwe baba bazze gyoli bakulamusa n'ekiramuso ekitali ekyo Katonda kyeyakutekerawo, nga bwe bagamba mu mitima gyaabwe nti lwaki Katonda tatubonereza olwebyo byetwogera. Omuliro Jahannama gwebagenda okuyingira gubamala. Nayo nno nkomerero mbi"
  58,9,Abange mmwe abakkiriza bwe mubanga muteesa mu kyama temuteesanga okukola ekibi kyonna oba obulabe oba okujeemera omubaka. Muteesenga byakukola bulungi nakutya Katonda. Era mutye Katonda anti gyali gyemugenda okukunganyirizibwa
  58,10,"Mazima okuteeseganya mu kyama mu ngeri embi n'okukola obulabe kikolwa kya Sitaane (nga nekigendererwa kye) kunyiiza bakkiriza. Ekyo tekiyinza kubaleetera kabi konna, okugyako nga Katonda akkirizza era abakkiriza bateekwa kwesiga Katonda yekka"
  58,11,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza bwe muba mugambiddwa nti mwefunze mu ntuula (ne banammwe bafune ebifo) mukikole. Katonda ajja ku basobozesa okugaziwa, ate bwe muba mugambiddwa okusituka (okuva mu kifo olwensonga yonna) musituke, anti Katonda asitula amadaala mu mmwe abakkiriza n'abo abaweebwa okumanya. Bulijjo Katonda mumanyi nnyo webyo byonna byemukola"
  58,12,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza bwemwagalanga okwogera n'omubaka musookenga ku saddaka, nga temunayogera naye. Ekyo kye kirungi gye muli era kyekisinga era kibatukuliza ddala. Naye bwe muba temulina kyemusadaka mazima Katonda musonyiyi waakisa"
  58,13,"Abaffe muzitowereddwa okuwaayo saddaka nga temunnaba kwogera ne Nabbi. Kale bwekibanga kibalemye oba nga ne Katonda abasonyiye, kale nno muyimirizeewo e sswala mutoole e zzaka mugondere Katonda n'omubakawe. Mazima Katonda amanyidde ddala nnyo ebyo byemukola"
  58,14,"Abaffe tewamanya abo abakwanagana n'abantu Katonda beyasunguwalira, abantu abo mu butuufu si ba mu mmwe wadde si ba mu bali (Bebakwanagana nabo) nebatuuka n'okulayira ku bulimba nga ate ddala bamanyi (ekituufu)"
  58,15,"Katonda yabategekera ebibonerezo ebikambwe, anti mazima byonna byebaakolanga bibi"
  58,16,"(Okulayira kwabwe nti basiramu) baakifuula ekyokuwona, olwo nno nebaziyiza abantu okukola emirimu gya Katonda, bagenda kutuukibwako ebibonerezo ebinyomesa"
  58,17,Emaali yaabwe n'abaana baabwe tebigenda kubagasa naakamu mumaaso g'a Katonda. Abo be bantu bo mumuliro ab'okugubeeramu obugenderevu
  58,18,"Olunaku Katonda lwalibazuukiza bonna nebamulayirira nga bwebaabalayirira mmwe ku nsi nga balowooza nti kyebakoze kyakubagasa. Abange, abo nno beebalimba bennyini"
  58,19,Sitaane yabeefunza okutuusa lweyabeerabiza okwogera ku Katonda. Abo nno be bagoberezi ba Sitaane. Mukimanye nti mazima ab'ekibiina kya Sitaane be b'okufafaganirwa
  58,20,Mazima abo abawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe ba mu bantu abanyoomebwa
  58,21,(Katonda) yakakasa dda nti nze Katonda n'ababaka bange tuli baakuwangula anti Katonda wamaanyi. Nnantakubwa ku mukono
  58,22,"Tewali bantu bonna abakkiriza Katonda n'olunaku lw’enkomerero baalibadde batiitiibya abo abawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe, kababe ba kitaabwe, oba baana baabwe, oba baganda baabwe, oba nga baaluganda lwabwe olwokumpi. Abo nno (abatakola ekyo) Katonda yatebenkeza obukkiriza mu mitima gyabwe, naabawagira naamanyi agava gyali era nga agenda kubayingiza e jjana egikulukutira wansi waazo emigga, nga bakubeera mu zo olubeerera. Katonda yabasiima nga nabo bwebaamusiima. Kisaana kimanyike nti mazima abo b'ebantu ba Katonda abokwesiimira ddala"
  59,1,"Ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi byonna bitendereza Katonda nantakubwa ku mukono, assa buli kintu mu ssa lyakyo"
  59,2,"Y'eyafulumya abo abaakafuwala mu bayudaaya (Ab'ekiika kya ba Banu Nadhiri) mu ngeri y'okubawangangusa okuva mu mayumba gaabwe olufuluma olwasooka. Temulowoozangako mmwe abakkiriza nti (ba Banu Nadhiri) bayinza okugobwa ate bo (ba Banu Nadhiri) baalowooza nti ebigo byabwe bijja kulemesa Katonda okubatuusaako ekyo kyayagala. Katonda nakibatuusaako mu kiseera webaali batakisuubirira. Era Katonda nateeka mu mitima gyabwe okutya okwensusso nga bo bennyini be bemenyera amayumba gaabwe n'emikono gyabwe, n'emikono gya bakkiriza negikola ekyo. Kale nno abategeera mumwe mugyemu ekyokuyiga"
  59,3,"Singa tekyali nti Katonda yabasalirawo ku bawangangusa yaalibadde ababonereza kuno ku nsi, ate nga ne ku nkomerero abategekedde ebibonerezo byomuliro"
  59,4,"Ekyo nno lwansonga yaakuba nti baawakanya Katonda n'omubakawe. Ate nga oyo yenna awakanya Katonda, amanye nti mazima Katonda muyitirivu waakubonereza"
  59,5,"Emiti gye ntende gyonna gyemwatema oba jemwaleka nga giyimiridde nga bwegyali, ebyo byonna byakolebwa lwa kiragiro kya Katonda, era alyoke aswaze abo abonoonyi"
  59,6,"Eyo emmaali Katonda gyeyasobozesa omubakawe okusuuza abalabe. (ba Banu Nadhiri) temwebagala nfaransi wadde engamiya okugenda gyebali. Wabula Katonda asobozesa ababakabe okuwangula oyo yenna gwaba ayagadde okuwangulwa, mazima Katonda asobola buli kintu kyonna"
  59,7,"Emmaali eyo yonna Katonda gyeyasobozesa omubakawe okusuuza okuva mu byalo (bya ba Banu Nadhiri ng'olutalo luggweredde mu kutegeeragana) eba y'a Katonda, n'omubakawe, n'aboluganda lwa Nabbi olwokumpi, ne ba mulekwa, ne ba masikiini, n'abatambuze naabo abafunye ebizibu mu ngendo zaabwe. Emmaali eyo ereme kuba nga abeegasa nayo bagagga bokka mu mmwe. Ebyo byonna omubaka byaba abaleetedde mubitwale. Ate ebyo byonna byaba abaziyizza mubireke mutye Katonda anti Katonda muyitirivu w'akubonereza"
  59,8,Na bwe kityo abaavu abaasenguka okuva e (Makkah) ne bagobwa mu mayumba gaabwe ne balesebwa e mmaali yaabwe nga banoonya obulungi n'okusiima kwa Katonda era nga baali bataasa ddiini y'a Katonda n'omubakawe (balinako omugabo). Abo nno b'ebakkiriza abamazima
  59,9,"Abatuuze b'e Madinah abaasooka okukkiriza obusiramu (ba Answar) baagala abo abaasengukira gyebali (ba Muhajiruuna), era tebalina nsaalwa yonna kwebyo ebyaweebwa bannabwe (ba Muhajiruna) era nga beeresa newakubadde nga balina obwetaavu bo bennyini. Omuntu awona omulugube, abo nno b'ebokwesiimira ddala"
  59,10,"Naabo abajja oluvanyuma lwabwe babasabira nga bagamba nti ayi Katonda tusonyiwe ne baganda baffe abaatukulembera mu bukkiriza, era tossa mu mitima gyaffe nsaalwa yonna eri abo abakkiriza. Ayi Katonda waffe gwe musaasizi oweekisa ekingi"
  59,11,Abaffe tolaba (ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) abananfunsi abagamba bannabwe abaakafuwala mu bayudaaya nti singa munaaba mugobeddwa naffe tujja kugenda nammwe. Era tetulikkiriza kigambo kyamuntu yenna ku bikwata ku mmwe. Era bwemulirwanyisibwa tugenda kubataasa. Ne Katonda akakasa nti mazima ddala baali balimba
  59,12,"Wabula singa (abayudaaya) bagobwa, abananfunsi tebagenda nabo. Ate ne bwebaba balwanyisiddwa tebabataasa. So nga ne bwebaba bagezezzaako okubataasa babaddukako, n'oluvanyuma nebatafuna kutaasibwa kwonna"
  59,13,"(Abakkiriza), mwe mutiibwa mu mitima gyabwe okusinga bwe batya Katonda. Ekyo nno lwakuba nti bbo kibiina ky'abantu abatategeera"
  59,14,"(Abayudaaya n'abananfunsi) tebayinza kubalwanyisa nga bali wamu okugyako nga bali mu byalo ebiriko ebigo, oba nga bali mabega w'abisenge. Obulabe wakati waabwe bokka buyitirivu obalowooza okuba nti bali wamu, so nga emitima gyaabwe myawukamu. Ekyo nno lwakuba nti bo kibiina kyabantu abatategeera"
  59,15,(Ba Banu Nadhiri) bafaanana naabo abaabakulembera e mabegako katono (Abakafiiri be Makkah abaawangulwa obubi ennyo ku lutalo lwe Badri) baaloza ku bukaawu bwe bikolwa byabwe (ku nsi) ate nga balinayo ebibonerezo ebiruma ennyo (ku nkomerero)
  59,16,"(Abananfunsi mu kusendasenda abayudaaya) balinga Sitaane bwe gamba omuntu nti kaafuwala. Wabula bwakaafuwala Sitaane emugamba nti nze siri naawe, mazima nze ntya Katonda omulezi w'ebitonde"
  59,17,"Enkomerero y'a bombi neeba nga ddala baakubeera mu muliro olubeerera, eyo nno y'empeera y'a beeyisa obubi"
  59,18,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza mutye Katonda, era omuntu atunule mu byategekedde olunaku lw'enkya. Bulijjo muteekwa okutya Katonda, anti mazima Katonda amanyidde ddala buli kye mukola"
  59,19,"Temubeera nga abo abaava ku Katonda, ekyavaako okuba nga Katonda abeerabiza bye baali bateekwa okwekolera, abo nno be bonoonyi"
  59,20,"Abantu bo mu muliro tebenkana na bantu ba mu jjana, abo abaliyingira e jjana be bokwesiima"
  59,21,"Singa twassa Kur'ani eno ku nsozi wandizirabye nga zigonze, era nga zimerenguse olw'okutya Katonda. Ebifaananyi ng'ebyo tubikubira abantu bibasoboseze okufumitiriza (bategeere Katonda)"
  59,22,"Yye Katonda, yooyo tewali kisinzibwa kyonna okugyako ye yekka, amanyi ebitalabwa n'ebirabwa. Yye yemusaasizi, oweekisa ekibuna kuno ku nsi, aliba n'ekisa ekyenjawulo ku lunaku lw'enkomerero"
  59,23,"Yye Katonda, yooyo tewali kisinzibwa kyonna okugyako yye, omufuzi wa buli kintu, atuukiridde mu buli kimu, kiwamirembe, akakasa obukkiriza bwa baddube, kalondoozi wa buli kintu, nantakubwa ku mukono, kkirimaanyi, kabwejungira. Katonda wanjawulo nnyo kwe byo bye bamugattako"
  59,24,"Yye Katonda, yooyo omutonzi, eyatandikawo ebitonde mu kubitonda nga talina kyalabirako, eyafaananya buli kintu nga bwa kyagala, alina amannya amalungi, buli ekiri mu ggulu n'ensi kimutendereza. Era yye Katonda, ye nantakubwa ku mukono, mugoba nsonga"
  60,1,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza temufuulanga abalabe bange era abalabe ba mmwe mikwano gyammwe egy'omunda, so nga baawakanya amazima agaabajjira okuva ewa Katonda ne bagobaganya omubaka awamu nammwe (okuva mu Makkah), olwokuba nti mukkiriza Katonda omulezi wa mmwe. Bwe muba mufulumye olw'okulwana mu kkubo lyange era nga munoonya okusiima kwange, (temukukutanga ne mubabuulira ebyama byammwe) nga mukolagana nabo mu ngeri y'ekyama ate nga nange manyi ebyo bye mukisa ne byemwolesa. Oyo yenna akikola mu mmwe aba avudde ku kkubo ettuufu"
  60,2,"Bwe babagwikiriza awantu wonna boolesa obulabe gye muli ne babagalulira emikono gyabwe (mu kubalwanyisa), era ne baboolekeza ennimi zaabwe (mu kubavuma) mu ngeri embi. Era nga beegomba nti singa mukaafuwadde"
  60,3,"Enganda zammwe wadde abaana ba mmwe tebagenda kubagasa ku lunaku lw'enkomerero. Katonda agenda kulamula wakati wa mmwe, anti Katonda alabira ddala ebyo bye mukola"
  60,4,"Mazima mulina ekyokulabirako ekirungi ekya Nabbi Ibrahim n'abakkiriza abaali naye, mu kiseera we baagambira bannaabwe nti mazima ffe tubesammudde n'ebyo bye musinza ebitali Katonda (ali omu). Tubawakanyizza era waliwo wakati waffe nammwe obulabe n'obukyayi obw'olubeerera, mpozzi nga mukkirizza Katonda ali omu. Okugyako ekigambo kya Ibrahim kye yagamba kitaawe oluberyeberye nti nja kwegayirira ddala Katonda akusonyiwe, era sirina kintu kyonna kyenyinza kukugasa ewa Katonda. Ayi Katonda waffe ggwe wekka gwetwesiga. Era tukwenenyerezza. Era gyoli gyetujja okudda"
  60,5,"Ayi Mukama Katonda waffe totufuula kikemo eri abo abaagaana okukkiriza era tusonyiwe ayi mukama waffe, anti mazima ggwe nantakubwa ku mukono, assa buli kintu mussa lyakyo"
  60,6,"Mazima mulina ekyokulabirako ekirungi ku bo (Nabbi Ibrahim n'abakkiriza abaali naye) ekyo kiri eri buli asuubira okufuna e mpeera okuva ewa Katonda ku lunaku lw'enkomerero. Naye oyo yenna anaaba akyuse (naava ku kukkiriza Katonda n'olunaku lw'enkomerero), mazima ddala Katonda yye talina kye yetaaga okuva eri bitondebye, atenderezebwa bulijjo"
  60,7,"Wabula Katonda asobola okussa wakati wa mmwe ne be muwalaggana nabo e nkolagana ennungi. Anti Katonda muyinza, era Katonda musonyiyi omusaasizi"
  60,8,"Katonda tabagaana ku kolagana naabo ababa tebabalwanyisizza olw'eddiini, era abatabagobaganya mu nsi yammwe mutuuke okuba nga temubayisa bulungi n'okubakolera obwenkanya, anti mazima Katonda ayagala abenkanya"
  60,9,"Mazima ddala Katonda abagaana okukolagana naabo abaabalwanyisa olw'eddiini, ne babagobaganya okuva mu nsi yammwe, ne bakola kinene nnyo mu kubagobaganya. Oyo yenna akolagana nabo, abo nno be balyazamanyi"
  60,10,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza singa abakyala abakkiriza babajjira nga basenguse mubagezesenga. Yye Katonda obukkiriza bwabwe aba abumanyi, bwe mukakasa nti bakkiriza temubaddizanga abakafiiri, abakyala bano tebali Halali ku bakafiiri abo nga n'abakafiiri abo bwe batali halali ku bakyala abo, wabula bo abasajja (Abakafiiri) mubaddize bye baawaayo mu kubawasa, olwo nno tekiba kibi bwe mubawasa nga mubawadde amahare gaabwe. Temwesiba ku kuwoowa okwekikafiiri kwe mwakola nabo. Mubasabe babaddize byemwawaayo nga nabo bwe basobola okusaba bye bawaayo. Ebyo nno kwe kulamula kwa Katonda kwabalamuza. Anti Katonda mumanyi nnyo ateeka buli kintu mussa lyakyo"
  60,11,Singa omukyala w'omu ku mmwe ava mu busiramu nadda mu bukafiiri kemulwanagana nabo ne mumala mufunayo eminyago muteekwa okusasula abo abaddukwako bakyala baabwe ekigero kyekyo kye bawaayo nga babawasa. Bulijjo muteekwa okuba nga mutya Katonda oyo gwemukkiriza
  60,12,"Owange ggwe Nabbi abakkiriza abakyala bwebajja gyoli nga bakuba ekirayiro mu maasogo, nti tebagenda kugatta ku Katonda kintu kyonna, era nga tebagenda kubba, wadde okwenda oba okutta abaana baabwe, era nti tebagenda kuwaayiriza nga bajingirira wakati w'emikono gyabwe n'amagulu gaabwe, nga era bwe batagenda kukujeemera mu kukola ekirungi kyonna, naawe nno bawe obukakafu era wegayirire Katonda abasonyiwe, anti mazima ddala Katonda musonyiyi nnyo omusaasizi"
  60,13,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza temukwanagana n'abantu Katonda beyasunguwalira. Anti bo tebalina ssuubi ku lunaku lw'enkomerero, nga abakafiiri bwebatalina ssuubi ku bikwata ku bantu abali emagombe"
  61,1,"Ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi byonna bitenda Katonda. Yye Katonda yemuwanguzi, assa buli kintu mu ssa lyakyo"
  61,2,Abange mmwe abakkiriza lwaki mwogera ebyo bye mutakola
  61,3,Kisunguwalirwa nnyo ewa Katonda okwogera bye mutakola
  61,4,"Mazima Katonda ayagala abo abalwana mu kkubolye, nga basimbye ennyiriri, ne baba nga ekizimbe, nga e bitundu byakyo bikwatagana bulungi"
  61,5,"Mu ngeri y'emu bajjukize ekyafaayo kya Musa bwe yagamba abantube nti, lwaki munnyiiza ng'ate mumanyidde ddala nti mazima nze ndi Mubaka wa Katonda gweyabatumira. Bwe baabula, Katonda kwekubuza emitima gyabwe, anti Katonda talungamya bantu bajeemu"
  61,6,"Era bajjukize e kyafaayo kya Isa mutabani wa Mariam bwe yagamba abaana ba Israel nti mazima nze ndi Mubaka wa Katonda gye muli, nga nkakasa Taurat eyankulembera era nga mpa amawulire ag'essanyu ag'omubaka alijja oluvanyuma lwange, nga erinyalye ye Ahmad. Wabula omubaka (Muhammad) oyo bwe yabajjira n'obubonero obunnyonnyofu, ate bo ne bagamba nti lino ddogo eryeyolefu"
  61,7,"Ani eyeeyisa obubi okusinga oyo atemerera Katonda ebyobulimba, so nga bulijjo ayitibwa okujja eri obusiramu. Katonda talungamya bantu abeeyisa obubi"
  61,8,(Mu kukola ekyo) baagala kuzikiza kitangaala kya Katonda n'emimwa gyabwe. Sso nga Katonda waakujjuza e kitangaalakye newakubadde nga abakafiiri tebakyagala
  61,9,Katonda yooyo eyatuma omubakawe ng'amuwadde obulungamu n'eddiini entuufu. Bulyoke bukye enkya nga yeddiini ewangudde newakubadde nga abagatta ku Katonda ebintu ebirala tebakyagala
  61,10,Abange mmwe abakkiriza mwandyagadde mbalagirire ebyettunzi ebiribawonya e bibonerezo ebiruma
  61,11,"(Nabyo) muteekwa okukkiriza Katonda n'omubakawe, ne mulafuubana mu kuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda, nga muwaayo emmaali yammwe, nga nammwe mwennyini mwenyigiramu. Ekyo nno kye kirungi gye muli singa mubadde mumanyi"
  61,12,"(Anti bwe mukola ebyo) Katonda ajja kubasonyiwa ebyonoono byammwe, abayingize e jjana ezikulukutiramu emigga era mugenda kufuna obutuulo obulungi mu jjana ez'olubeerera, okwo nno kwe kwesiima okusuffu"
  61,13,"Era mufune n'ekirala nga nakyo mukyagala, nakyo kwe kutaasa kwa Katonda n'obuwanguzi obwamangu. Era sanyusa abakkiriza (nti byonna bagenda kubifuna)"
  61,14,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza musituke mutaase e ddiini y'a Katonda. Kibe nga Issa mutabani wa Mariam bwe yagamba abagoberezibe abenjawulo nti, baani abanannyamba ku mulimu gwa Katonda. Abagoberezibe abenjawulo kwe kuddamu nti ffe twewaddeyo okutaasa e ddiini ya Katonda. Ekyavaako ogutundu ku baana ba Israel okukkiriza, n'ekitundu ekirala okukaafuwala. Naffe ne tutaasa abo abakkiriza ku mulabe waabwe, ne bukya enkya nga be bali waggulu"
  62,1,"Ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi byonna bitenda Katonda omufuzi wa buli kintu, omutukuvu mu buli kimu, nantakubwa ku mukono, assa buli kintu mussa lyakyo"
  62,2,Yye yooyo eyatuma eri abo abataamanya kusoma na kuwandiika omubaka (Muhammad) nga ava mu bo ng'abasomera e bigambo bya Katonda era nga abatukuza (okubajja mu bukafiiri) era nga abayigiriza ekitabo (Kur'ani) n'ebiva mu Hadith so nga oluberyeberye (nga Nabbi tannatumwa) baali mu bubuze obw'olwatu
  62,3,"Era yamutuma n'eri abalala nga ba mu bo, naye nga balijja luvannyuma lwabwe (nabo be basiramu abalala bonna abakkiriza Nabbi Muhammad abataamulabako okutuusiza ddala ku lunaku lw'enkomerero) era yye Katonda, ye nantakubwa ku mukono, assa buli kintu mussa lyakyo"
  62,4,Ebyo bye birungi bya Katonda byawa oyo gwaba ayagadde. Mazima Katonda ye nannyini birungi ebisukkulumu
  62,5,"Ekifaananyi kyabo abaaweebwa Taurat ne batagikozesa, balinga endogoyi ey'etikka ebitabo (nga tesobola kwe gasa nabiri mu bitabo ebyo), kibi nnyo ekifaananyi ekyo, ekyabo abalimbisa ebigambo bya Katonda. Bulijjo Katonda talungamya bantu beeyisa bubi"
  62,6,"Bagambe (ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti abange mmwe abayudaaya bwe muba nga mweyita abaagalwa ba Katonda (mwe mwekka) so ssi abantu abalala, kale nno mwegombe okufa bwe muba nga muli ba mazima"
  62,7,"Tebagenda kwe gombera ddala kufa, olwebyo byebaakola. Bulijjo Katonda amanyi nnyo abeeyisa obubi"
  62,8,"Bagambe (ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti mazima okwo okufa kwe mudduka kwakubatuukako, oluvanyuma muzzibwe eri omumanyi w'ebitalabikako n'ebirabika. Ate nno olwo alyoke abategeeze ebyo byonna bye mwali mukola"
  62,9,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza, bwe baaziinanga olw'esswala (ye jjuma) ku lunaku lwe jjuma, mwanguwenga okugenda eri okwogera ku Katonda, ate muyimirize emirimu. Ekyo kye kirungi gye muli singa mubadde mumanyi"
  62,10,"E sswala bweggwa, olwo nno mugende mu nsi munoonye ebigabwa bya Katonda, mwogere nnyo ku Katonda mulyoke mwesiime"
  62,11,"Bwe balaba ebyo busuubuzi, oba ebya masanyu, banguwa okugenda gyebiri ne bakuleka nga oyimiridde. Bagambe nti ebya Katonda bye birungi okusinga ebya masanyu n'obusuubuzi, ate nga Katonda yaasinga abagabi bonna"
  63,1,"Abannanfusi bwe bajja gyoli (Ggwe Nabbi Muhammad (ﷺ)) bagamba nti tukkiriza nti mazima ddala ggwe oli Mubaka wa Katonda. Ne Katonda akimanyidde ddala nti mazima gwe oli Mubakawe, ate era Katonda akakasa nti mazima abannanfusi balimba nnyo"
  63,2,"Ekyo kulayira kwabwe (nti basiramu) bakifuula ekyokulwanyisa ekibawonya, olwonno ne balyoka baziyiza abantu okuyingira mu ddiini y'a Katonda. Mazima bibi nnyo ebyo bye baali bakola"
  63,3,"Ekyo kiri bwe bityo lwa kuba baalangirira obukkiriza n'ennimi za bwe, so nga munda bakafiiri. Olwo nno e mitima gyabwe negiteekebwako envumbo ne babeera nga tebategeera"
  63,4,"Bwo batunulako, e mibiri gyabwe gikusanyusa, bwe boogera toyinza butatwala kigambo kyabwe, balinga ebiti ebyesigamiziddwa ku kisenge nga tebiyinza kwetengerera, buli lwonna lwe bawulira akakuba bagamba nti bubakeeredde, abo be balabe, n'olwekyo beegendereze, Katonda yabakolimira, ggwe ate bandivudde batya ku mazima"
  63,5,"Singa baba bagambiddwa nti mujje eri omubaka wa Katonda abasabire e kisonyiwo, banyeenya e mitwe n'obalabira ddala nga bajeemye era nga beekuluntazza"
  63,6,"Okubasabira e kisonyiwo n'obutabasabira byonna bifaanana, Katonda tagenda kubasonyiwa, anti Katonda talungamya bantu boononyi"
  63,7,Be bamu be bo abagamba nti temuwaayo kintu kyonna eri abo abali awamu n'omubaka wa Katonda okutuusa lwe banamwabulira. So nga amawanika g'omuggulu n'ensi gonna ga Katonda. Naye mazima abananfusi tebategeera
  63,8,Baatuuka n'okugamba nti bwe tunadda e Madinah (okuva mu lutalo lwa ba Bani Al Mus-twalik) abasinga okuba ab'ekitiibwa bajja kugoba mu (Madinah) abanyoomebwa. So nga e kitiibwa n'obuwanguzi bya Katonda n'omubakawe n'abakkiriza naye mazima abananfusi tebamanyi
  63,9,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza, ebyo bugagga byamwe n'abaana bamwe tebibawugulanga ne bibajja ku kwogera ku Katonda, oyo yenna akikola, abo nno be bokufaafaaganirwa"
  63,10,"Era mugabe kwe byo bye twabawa walumbe nga tannatuuka ku omu ku mmwe, naatuuka okulaajana nga agamba nti, ayi mukama omulezi wange singa ondeseewo akabanga ne nsadaakako era ne mbeera mu balongoofu"
  63,11,"Sso nga Katonda tagenda kulindiriza mwoyo gwonna entuuko yaagwo bweriba nga etuuse, Katonda bulijjo muyitirivu w'akumanya ebyo byonna bye mukola"
  64,1,"Ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi byonna bitenda Katonda, obufuzi bwonna n'amatendo gonna bibye, anti ye muyinza wa buli kintu"
  64,2,Yye yooyo eyabatonda nga mu mmwe mulimu abakafiiri na bandi bakkiriza. Lubeerera Katonda alaba bye mukola
  64,3,Yatonda eggulu n'ensi lwa nsonga. Ekifaananyi kye yabatonderako kye kisingira ddala okuba ekirungi. Era gyali gye mugenda okudda
  64,4,"Amanyi ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi, era nga bwa manyi bye mukweka ne bye mwolesa. Anti Katonda amanyi ebiri mu bifuba"
  64,5,"Abaffe amawulire gaabo abaakafuwala oluberyeberye lwa mmwe tegaabatuukako, ekyabaviirako okuba nga bakomba ku bukaawu bwo bukafiri bwabwe. Era bagenda kutuukwakwo e bibonerezo ebiruma"
  64,6,"Olwe'nsonga nti ababaka baabwe baabaleeteranga obubaka obujjudde obunnyonnyofu, bo ne bagamba nti omuntu obuntu yajja atulungamye! ekyo ne kibakaafuwaza, ne baba nga tebakyayagala kuwulira kikwata ku bubaka, ne Katonda naaba nga takyabeetaaga. Anti Katonda bulijjo talina kye yataaga, era nga bulijjo atenderezebwa"
  64,7,"Abatakkiriza Katonda beerimba nga bagamba nti tebagenda kuzuukizibwa. Bagambe ggwe (Nabbi Muhammad (ﷺ)) nti ssi bwekiri. Ndayira Katonda omulezi wange ddala mujja kuzuukizibwa, oluvanyuma mujja kutegeezebwa ddala ebyo bye mwakola, nekyo nno kyangu nnyo ku Katonda"
  64,8,"Kale nno mukkirize Katonda n'omubakawe n'ekitangaala (Kur'ani) kye twassa, ne Katonda bulijjo mumanyi nnyo weebyo bye mukola"
  64,9,"Mujjukire olunaku Katonda lwa libakunganya ku lunaku lwe kiyaama, olwo lwe lunaku oluliraga okufaafaganirwa (eri abakafiiri), oyo yenna akkiriza Katonda naakola e mirimu emirungi, Katonda amusangulako ebibibye, era agenda kumuyingiza e jjana ezikulukutiramu e migga, nga baakuzibeeramu lubeerera. Okwo nno kwe kwe siima okuyitirivu"
  64,10,"Naye ate abo abaakafuwala ne balimbisa n'ebigambo byaffe, abo nno b'ebantu bo mu muliro, ba kubeera mu gwo olubeerera, eyo nkomerero mbi"
  64,11,"Tewali buzibu bwonna butuuka ku muntu okugyako nga Katonda akkirizza, oyo yenna akkiriza Katonda, Katonda alungamya omutimagwe. Mazima bulijjo Katonda mumanyi nnyo wa buli kintu"
  64,12,"Mugondere Katonda era mugondere omubakawe. Naye bwe munaayawukana kwe kyo, ye omubaka waffe (tanenyezebwa) obuvunaanyizibwabwe, kwe kutuusa obubaka mu bujjuvu"
  64,13,"Katonda ye yekka asinzibwa, abakkiriza bateekwa kwesiga Katonda yekka"
  64,14,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza mazima mu bakyala ba mmwe n'abaana ba mmwe mulimu abalabe, n'olwekyo mubeegendereze. Naye bwe mubaddiramu ne mubalekera, ne mubasonyiwa, mazima Katonda muyitirivu waakusonyiwa asaasira ennyo"
  64,15,"Mazima e byobugagga bya mmwe n'abaana ba mmwe kikemo, ng'ate ewa Katonda we wali empeera ensukkulumu"
  64,16,"Kale nno mutye Katonda nga bwe muba musobodde, muwulire era mugonde, mu ngeri yeemu mugabe ku lwa Katonda, ekyo nno kye kirungi gye muli. Oyo yenna awonyezebwa omulugube gwo mwoyogwe, abo nno be b'okuganyulwa"
  64,17,"Singa muwola Katonda oluwola olulungi, alubabalizaamu era n'abasonyiwa ebyonoono bya mmwe, bulijjo Katonda asiima era wa kisa"
  64,18,"(Katonda oyo) amanyi ebitalabwako n'ebirabwa, nantalemwa, akola buli kintu nga asinziira ku nsonga"
  65,1,"Owange ggwe Nabbi, bwe muba nga muta abakyala, mubate nga bali ku mbeera eyobutukuvu (Nga tebali mu Haidh), mubalenga n'obwegendereza ebbanga lya Idda (Idda kye kiseera omukyala ateereddwa kyamala nga tannaba ku kkirizibwa kuddamu kufumbirwa). Era mutye Katonda omulezi wa mmwe, temwetantalanga okubaggya mu mayumba gaabwe (mwe babadde bawangaalira nga bali mu bufumbo bwa bwe), so nga nabo tebavanga mu mayumba ago okugyako nga bakoze ebikolobero eby'olwatu. Ezo z'ensalo z'amateeka ga Katonda. Oyo yenna abuuka ensalo z'amateeka ga Katonda, aba y'eryazaamanyizza, tomanya oba olyawo Katonda naaleetawo embeera endala oluvanyuma lw'ekyo"
  65,2,"Kale nno bwe baba nga basemberedde okumalako ebbanga lya Idda yaabwe mubaddirengamu, mu ngeri ennungi, oba mwawukane nabo mu ngeri ennungi (ebbanga lya Idda bwe riba liweddeko). Mubeerewo n'abajulizi babiri abeesimbu mu bantu ba mmwe, muwenga obujulizi mu bwe simbu kulwa Katonda, ebyo nno bibuulirirwa nabyo oyo yenna akkiriza Katonda n'olunaku lw'enkomerero. Bulijjo oyo yenna atya Katonda amuteerawo obwangu"
  65,3,"Era naamugabirira mu ngeri gyatasuubira, era oyo yenna eyeesiga Katonda, Katonda amumala, anti Katonda ekigambokye kye kyenkomeredde, mazima Katonda yategeka ekigero kya buli kintu"
  65,4,"Abo bonna mu bakyala ba mmwe abatakyagenda mu nsonga za Heidh, bw emutankananga ebbanga lya Idda yaabwe, balindenga emyezi esatu. Wabula abo abatanayingira mu nsonga za Haidh Idda yaabwe emyezi esatu. Naye abo abali embuto ebbanga lyabwe kumala kuzaala. Oyo yenna atya Katonda amuteerawo obwangu mu buli kintu"
  65,5,"Ekyo kiragiro kya Katonda kye yassa gye muli, oyo yenna atya Katonda amusangulako e bibibye ate naamwongeza e mpeera"
  65,6,"(Abakyala abaweereddwa ttalaka) mu basuzenga mu mayumba mwe musula okusinziira ku busobozi bwa mmwe, temubatulugunyanga, nga ekigendererwa kubanyigiriza (balemererwe), naye bwe babanga bali mbuto mubalabirirenga okutuusa lwe bazaala. Ate (bwe babanga bazadde) nebabayonseza abaana, mubasasulenga. Era mukkiriziganye mu ngeri e nnungi, naye bwe mubanga mulemaganye olwo nno munoonye omulala anaayonsa"
  65,7,"Omusajja alina okulabirira omukyala okusinziira ku busobozibwe, nooyo Katonda gwe yawa ebyenfuna ebinafu naye alabirira omukyala okusinziira nga Katonda bwe yamuwa, Katonda tawaliriza muntu yenna okusukka kwe byo bye yamuwa. Katonda ajja kuteekawo obwangu oluvanyuma lwo buzito"
  65,8,"Ebitundu bimeka nga abantu baayo bajeemera Katonda omulezi waabwe n'ababaka beyabatumiranga, ne tubibala olubala oluyitirivu era ne tubibonereza olubonereza olukambwe"
  65,9,"(Ebitundu ebyo) ne bikomba ku bukaawu bw'obujeemu bw'abyo, n'eba nga enkomerero y'obujeemu bwabwe kufaafaganirwa"
  65,10,"Katonda yabategekera ebibonerezo ebikambwe, kale nno mutye Katonda abange mmwe abalina amagezi agategeera, abange mmwe abakkiriza. Anti Katonda yassa gye muli obubaka obujjukiza (Kur'ani)"
  65,11,"Omubaka nga abasomera ebigambo bya Katonda ebinnyonnyola, nga ekigendererwa kwe kugya mu bizikiza abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi n'abazza mu kitangaala. Oyo yenna akkiriza Katonda n'akola e mirimu e mirungi, Katonda agenda kumuyingiza mu jjana, nga e migga gikulukutira muzo, baakubeera muzo olubeerera. (Omuntu ow'engeri eyo) Katonda yamutebenkereza enfuna (mu bulamu obwo luvannyuma)"
  65,12,"Katonda yooyo eyatonda eggulu omusanvu n'ensi naazitonda omuwendo gwe gumu, obubaka bwa Katonda bukka wakati we ggulu n'ensi mulyoke mumanye nti, mazima Katonda musobozi ku buli kintu, era mazima Katonda mumanyi wa buli kintu"
  66,1,"Owange ggwe Nabbi lwaki oziza ebyo Katonda bye yakukkiriza, nga onoonya okusiimisa bakyalabo. Bulijjo Katonda muyitirivu wa kusonyiwa era muyitirivu wa kusaasira"
  66,2,"Katonda yabateerawo engeri gye muva mu birayiro byemuba mukoze, anti bulijjo aba nammwe, ate nga yye muyitirivu wa kumanya, buli kyakola akikola lwa nsonga"
  66,3,"Era jjukira Nabbi bwe yabuulira omu ku bakyalabe (Hafuswa) ekyama, omukyala oyo bwe yamala okwogera ekyama ekyo, ate Katonda n'akitegeeza Nabbi. Nabbi n'amubuulirako ebimu ebirala n'abireka. Nabbi olwa kibuulira omukyala oyo (omukyala n'amubuuza) nti ani yakikugambye (Nabbi n'amuddamu nti) eyakintegeezezza ye muyitirivu w'okumanya omukenkufu (Katonda)"
  66,4,"Singa munaaba mwenenyezza mwembiriri (Hafuswa ne Aisha) ewa Katonda (kye kirungi gye muli), anti emitima gya mmwe gyawaganyadde. Naye bwe munamwekalakaasizaako, (mumanye nti) mazima Katonda ali ku luddalwe, ne Jiburilu, n'abakkiriza abalongoofu, ne ba Malayika bonna oluvanyuma lw'ekyo ba kumuyambako"
  66,5,"Singa anaba abatadde, Katonda omuleziwe, ajja kumuwaanyisizaamu abakyala abalala abasinga ku mmwe, nga basiramu nnyo, bakkirizza, nga bagonvu nnyo, nga beenenya era nga basinza nnyo Katonda, abatambulira mu kumutya, kababe nga baafumbirwako oba nga tebafumbirwangako"
  66,6,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza mwewonye muwonye n'abantu ba mmwe omuliro, nga gukumirwa ku bantu na mayinja, gukuumibwa ba Malayika abakambwe abaamanyi ennyo, tebajeemera Katonda mu kyonna kyaba abalagidde, ate nga bakola ekyo kyonna kye baba balagiddwa"
  66,7,"(Ku lunaku lw'enkomerero abakafiiri baligambibwa nti) Abange mmwe abakafiiri temwetonda olwaleero, mazima mugenda kusasulwa ebyo bye mwakola"
  66,8,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza mwenenyeze Katonda olwenenya olwa namaddala. Omulezi wa mmwe Katonda kikakafu ajja ku basangulako ebyonoono bya mmwe era abayingize e jjana ezikulukutirwamu e migga. Olunaku Katonda lwataliweebuula Nabbi na bakkiriza abali naye. E kitangaala kyabwe nga kibeetoolodde mu maaso ne ku ddyo waabwe, nga bagamba nti ayi omulezi waffe tulekerewo e kitangaala kyaffe era otusonyiwe (ebyonoono byaffe) anti mazima ggwe oli musobozi ku buli kintu"
  66,9,"Owange ggwe Nabbi funvubira mu kulwanyisa abakafiiri n'abannanfusi era obazitoowereze. Obuddo bwabwe muliro Jahannama, ate obuddo obwo bubi nnyo"
  66,10,"Katonda yakubira abakafiiri ekifananyi kya muka Nuhu ne muka Luutu. Baali bakyala b'a baddu ababiri mu baddu baffe abalongoofu, naye nno ne babakumpanya (n'obutakkiriza Katonda). Nabbi Nuhu ne Luutu tebaalina kye baagasa bakyala baabwe ewa Katonda. Ne bagambwa (Abakyala bombi) nti muyingire omuliro awamu naabo abaguyingira"
  66,11,"Era Katonda yakubira abakkiriza e kifaananyi kya muka Firawo mu kiseera weyasabira (Katonda) nti: Ayi omulezi wange nzimbirayo e nyumba gyoli mu jjana era omponye Firawo n'ebikolwabye, omponye n'abantu abeeyisa obubi"
  66,12,"Era Katonda yakuba e kifananyi kya Mariyamu muwala wa Imran oyo eyeekuuma kale netufuuwa mu ye omwoyo ogwava gye tuli era Mariam nakkiriza ebigambo bya Katondawe n'ebitabobye, n'abeera nga ali mu basinza Katonda abagonvu"
  67,1,"Mukama Katonda nanyini buyinza bwonna musukkulumu, era nga muyinza w'abuli kintu"
  67,2,"Oyo eyatonda okufa n'obulamu, olwokubageseza alabe ani asinga okukola obulungi. Naye ye Nnantakubwa ku mukono omusonyiyi"
  67,3,"Oyo eyatonda eggulu omusanvu nga myaliro, toyinza kulaba mu kutonda kwa Katonda kamogo konna w'etegereze abaffe olabamu obukyamu bwonna"
  67,4,Era zzaayo amaaso emirundi nemirundi eriiso lijja ku kuddira nga likooye era nga tolina kyofunyeeyo
  67,5,"Mazima eggulu eriri okumpi n'ensi twalinyiriza nemunyeeye ezaaka, era nga bitawuliro ebigoba Sitani era Sitani ezo twazitegekera ebibonerezo byomuliro Ssair"
  67,6,Ate bbo abaawakanya Katonda waabwe twabategekera ebibonerezo byamuliro Jahannama era buliba buddo bubi
  67,7,Bwe baligusuulwamu bagenda kuguwulira nga gutokota era nga gufuuwa
  67,8,Nga gubula kuyulikamu buli lwegunasulwangamu ekibinja abakuumi bagwo banababuuzanga nti temwajjirwa muntu yenna abatiisa (muliro guno)
  67,9,"Baliddamu nti weewawo omutiisa yatujjira naye netumulimbisa era netumugamba nti Katonda tassanga bubaka bwonna, ebyo byemulimu bubuze obuyitirivu"
  67,10,Baligamba nti singa twali tuwulira oba nga tutegeera (ebyatugambwanga) tetwandibadde bamu kwabo abayingira omuliro
  67,11,Nebeekakasaako ekyonoono kyabwe okufaafaganirwa kuli ku bantu bo mu muliro
  67,12,"Mazima abo abatya Katonda wabwe awamu n'okuba nga talabika, bagenda okufuna ekisonyiwo n'empeera ensuffu"
  67,13,Kyekimu mukwese ebigambo byamwe oba mubyatudde mazima yye amanyi ebiri mu bifuba
  67,14,Abaffe eyatonda ayinza obutamanya nga ate ye muyitirivu w'okumanya era nga mukugu nnyo
  67,15,"Yye yoyo eyabafuulira ensi enyangu, kale mutambule mu bitundu byayo mulye mu bigabwabye era gyali gye mugenda okudda"
  67,16,Musuubidde okuwona oyo ali waggulu ensi n'etabamira singa eba etabanguse
  67,17,"Oba musuubidde okuwona oyo ali waggulu n'atabasindikira muyaga, wabula mugenda kumanya okulabula kwange nga bwekwali okukulu"
  67,18,"Abo abaaliwo oluberyeberye lwabwe baalimbisa, naye tewamanya kyennabatusaako"
  67,19,"Abaffe tebalaba ebinyonyi ebibuukira waggulu wabwe nga byanjuluza ebiwawaatiro ate nga n'oluusi biwumbako, tewali kibikuumira mu bbanga okugyako Katonda omusaasizi, mazima ye alaba buli kintu"
  67,20,"Oba ani oyo asobola okubalwanirira n'abataasa atali Katonda, abawakanyi tebalina kyebaliko okugyako mawaggali"
  67,21,Ye abaffe ani oyo ayinza okubagabirira singa Katonda abajjako okugabirirakwe. Wabula baagwa mu kateebe k'okuwalaaza empaka n'okwewaggula
  67,22,Ye abaffe oyo atambula abwamiridde ku kyenyikye y'abeera kubulungamu oba oyo atambula nga yeegolodde ngali ku Kkubo eggolokofu
  67,23,Bagambe nti Katonda y'eyabatandikawo n'abassako amatu n'amaaso n'abawa n'emitima wabula mwebaza kitono
  67,24,Bagambe nti Katonda yoyo eyabassa mu nsi era nga mugenda kuzuukizibwa mudde gyali
  67,25,Bagamba mu kubalaata nti ebyo byemutulaganyisa biribaawo ddi bwe mubanga byemwogera bituufu
  67,26,"Bagambe nti okumanya okujjuvu okukwata ku nsonga eyo kuli wa Katonda, naye nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu"
  67,27,"Bwe baliraba e bibonerezo nga bisembedde, ebyenyi byabo abakafuwala bigenda kwekaba, awo balyoke bategezebwe nti ekyo nno kye mwagambanga nti kirituukaddi"
  67,28,"Bagambe nti, mulaba mutya singa Katonda anzikiriza n'abo abali nange oba n'atusaasira anti obuyinza bwonna buli gyali, naye ani alitaasa abakafiiri ku bibonerezo ebiruma"
  67,29,Bagambe nti yye Katonda omusaasizi gwetukkiriza era yekka gwetwesiga wabula lumu mulimanya ani ali mu bubuze obweyolefu
  67,30,Bagambe nti mulaba mutya singa amazzi gammwe bukya nga gakalidde ani ayinza okubawa amazzi agakulukuta amayonjo
  68,1,"Nuni, yemu kunyukuta ezikola walifu empalabu. Ndayidde e kalamu nebyebagiwandiisa"
  68,2,Mazima Gwe Muhammad ekyengera kyobwa Nabbi Katonda wo kyeyakuwa tekiyinza ku kufuula mulalu
  68,3,Era ddala oteekwa okufuna empeera etakutukawo
  68,4,Era mazima ddala Ggwe oli wampisa nungi nnyo
  68,5,Ojja kulaba nga nabo bwebagenda okulaba
  68,6,Ani kumwenna eyatukwako ekizibu kyeddalu
  68,7,Mazima Katondawo amanyidde ddala ani eyabula okuva ku kkubolye era nga bwamanyidde ddala abalungamu
  68,8,Kale nno togondera abo abalimbisa
  68,9,Bandyagadde nti singa obagondera nabo nebakugondera
  68,10,Era togeza n'ogondera buli alayiralayira ataliimu nsa
  68,11,Omugeyi atambuza olugambo
  68,12,"Omukodo, omulumbaganyi omwononefu"
  68,13,Mubi nnyo ate awamu n'ekyo mwana w'abwenzi
  68,14,Tomugondera olwokuba alina emmali n'abaana
  68,15,Omuntu oyo bwasomerwa ebigambo byaffe agamba nti nfumo z'abantu abedda
  68,16,Kulunaku lw’enkomerero tugenda kussa kunyindo ye akabonero akamulamba nga tanayingizibwa muliro
  68,17,"Mazima ffe twagezesa abantu be Makkah bwetwabaleetera enjala nga bwetwagezesa abantu abaalina enimiro yaabwe abalayira nti baali bagenda kukungula kumakya nnyo, olwo nno baleme kugabirako bantu balala"
  68,18,Wabula beerabira okugamba nti Insh'allah
  68,19,Katonda n'agisindikira nabbambula w'omuliro ogwa gizikiriza ekiro nga beebase
  68,20,Okugenda okukya ngankalu nga enkungule
  68,21,Ku lunaku olulaganye baakeera nnyo era nga buli omu agenda atemya kumunne
  68,22,Ngabagamba nti muzuukuke mugende mu nimiro yammwe bwe muba ddala nga munakungula nga bwemwagambye
  68,23,Baatambula nga bogera bwama
  68,24,Nga bwebagamba nti tebagenda kukkiriza Masikiini yenna kuyingira mu ssamba yaabwe
  68,25,Baatambula kumakya okwo nga bakakasa nti bagenda kutuukiriza kyebaali basazeewo eggulo limu
  68,26,Bwebaalaba ennimiro yaabwe b'agamba nti tubuze
  68,27,Sinakindi Katonda yagizikirizza olwe kigendererwa kyaffe ekibi ekyobutakkiriza kugabirako ba Masikiini
  68,28,"Eyali abasingako eddiini n'obuntu bulamu nabagamba nti ssabagambye nti obutawaako banaku buba bulyazamanyi bwennyini, era kati kyetuteekwa okukola kwekutendereza Katonda kuba tetunamanya yatusonyiye oba nedda"
  68,29,Olwo nno nebagamba nti yayawukana Katonda waffe mazima twabadde tweyisizza bubi
  68,30,Awamu nekyo baatandika okuwaanyisiganya ebigambo nga abamu banenya bannabwe
  68,31,Nebagamba nti mazima ffe tubadde bajeemu
  68,32,"Tusaba Katonda waffe emmali yaffe etokomose atuwanyisizeemu ebirungi, mazima ddala ew'a Katonda waffe yokka gyetusaba obuyambi"
  68,33,Bwebityo nno ebibonerezo bwebiba naye wabula ebibonerezo by'olunaku lw’enkomerero byebisinga obukakali singa baba ddala nga bamanyi
  68,34,Mazima abatya Katonda baategekerwa e jjana ez'ebyengera ewa Katonda waabwe
  68,35,Gwe ate abakkiriza twalibayisizza nga abonoonyi
  68,36,"Mwaba ki, e nsonga muzisalawo mutya"
  68,37,Simanyi mulinayo ekitabo mwemubisoma
  68,38,Era nga mukitaba ekyo mulimu nti mwe mulyesalirawo kyemwagala ku lunaku lw'enkomerero
  68,39,Oba mulina e ndagano gye twabawa nga etuukira ddala ku lunaku lw'enkomerero ngebawa ebbeetu okwesalirawo nga bwemulaba
  68,40,Babuuze ani eyesowolayo abe nga akulembera endowooza eyo
  68,41,"Oba balinayo (ababeesiguza) nga babayita babeezi ba Katonda, kale nno bajjanga nabo bwebaba nga bogera mazima"
  68,42,Ku lunaku olulibeera olw'okubikkula ku ntumbwe. Balikowoolwa okuvunnamira Katonda naye nga tebasobola
  68,43,"Nga amaaso gaabwe makakkamu olw'obuswavu, nga bajjudde okunyomebwa so nga ate baakowolwa okuvunnamira Katonda nga bakyali balamu ne batakikola"
  68,44,Kale ndeka noyo alimbisa ebigambo bino tujja kubatwaliriza mpola mpola nga tebamanyi
  68,45,"Era mbalindiriza, anti entegeka zange nnywevu"
  68,46,Abaffe wali obasabye empeera nebakaluubirirwa kusasula
  68,47,"Oba bamanyi ebyewala nga babiwandiika (nga bebyelamuza, era nga biraga nti bagenda kubeera bulungi)"
  68,48,"Kale nno beera mugumikiriza ku kusalawo kwa Katondawo, tobeera nga ow'ekyennyanja (Nabbi Yunus) eyatuuka okukowoola (Katondawe okumutaasa) nga ajjudde obunyiikaavu"
  68,49,Singa teyafuna kyengera ekyava ewa Katondawe (ekyokukiriza okwenenyakwe) yandikasukiddwa mu nsi e nkalu (etariiko bulamu) nga naye anenyezebwa
  68,50,Wabula Katonda yamulekera obwa Nabbi era namuteeka mu bantu abalongofu
  68,51,Abakafiiri basemberera ddala okukuzikiriza n'amaaso gaabwe amabi (olw'ekkonda eriri ku myoyo gyabwe) bwe bawulira Kur'ani era ne bagamba nti mazima yye (Nabbi) mulalu
  68,52,So ng'ate (Kur'ani) teri okugyako kya kujjukiza eri e bitonde
  69,1,Olunaku olwokwolesa amazima (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  69,2,Olunaku lwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,3,Naye omanyi olunaku olwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,4,Abantu ba Thamud n'aba A'adi baalimbisa olunaku olwentiisa
  69,5,Abantu ba Thamud bazikirizibwa nakubwatuka okwamanyi
  69,6,Ate ba A'adi nebazikirizibwa nakibuyaga owamanyi ennyo eyalimu obunyogovu
  69,7,"Gweyabamazaamu ebiro musanvu nenaku munaana awatali kuyimiriramu, walaba abantu nga bagudde eri nga balinga enduli zemitende ezikutuddwako amasanso"
  69,8,Gwe mu kulaba waliwo eyawona
  69,9,"Farawo, n'abamukulembera, naabo abali kubyalo bya Luutu bayonoona"
  69,10,Ekyatuusa buli bamu okujeemera omubaka Katonda gwe yabatumira. Katonda kye yava abakwata olukwata oluyitirivu
  69,11,Aba Nuhu amazzi bwegaabooga okubawonya twabasaabaliza mulyato
  69,12,Olwo nno tulyoke tukibafuulire mmwe ekyokwebuulirira era gakitegeere amatu agategeera
  69,13,Naye engombe bwerifuyibwa olufuuwa olusooka
  69,14,Ensi nensozi birisitulwa nebimementulwa omulundi gumu
  69,15,Olwo nno olunaku lw’enkomerero luliba lutuuse
  69,16,"Eggulu ligenda kweyasaamu, nga ku lunaku olwo ligenda kuba lyabirivu"
  69,17,"Nga ba Malayika bali kumabbali galyo, nga waggulu waabwe kulunaku olwo ba Malayika munaana beebalisitula Arishi y'amukama Katonda wo"
  69,18,Ku lunaku olwo mugenda kuleetebwa mubalibwe tewali kintu kyonna kyemukola kigenda kwekweka
  69,19,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwaddyo agenda kugamba nti abange mujje musome ekitabo kyange
  69,20,Mazima nali nkakasa nti ngenda kubalibwa
  69,21,Oyo nno agenda kubeera mu bulamu obwesiimisa
  69,22,Mu jjana ey'a waggulu
  69,23,Ebibala byayo nga birengejjera kumpi
  69,24,Kale mulye era munywe muyogeyoge olwebyo byemwakulembeza mu nnaku ezaayita
  69,25,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwa kkono aligamba nti zinsanze singa siwereddwa kitabo kyange
  69,26,Era nessimanya kubalibwa kwange
  69,27,Waakiri singa bwennafa kyekyamala nessizuukira
  69,28,Ebyobugagga byange tebingasizza
  69,29,Sikyalina byakuwoza
  69,30,Mu kiseera ekyo Katonda agenda kulagira nti mumukwate mumulijje
  69,31,Bwemumala mumukasuke mu muliro
  69,32,Bwemumala mumuyiseemu olujegere oluwanvu bwalwo obwenkana emikono nsanvu
  69,33,Anti yali takkiriza Katonda owekitiibwa
  69,34,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  69,35,N'olwekyo olwaleero wano talinawo muntu amulumirwa
  69,36,Nga bwatalina kyakulya okugyako masirasira
  69,37,Ebintu ebitayinza kulibwa okugyako abonoonyi
  69,38,Tewali kingana kulayira ebyo byemulaba
  69,39,Nebyo byemutalaba
  69,40,Mazima Kur'ani bigambo bya Katonda byeyassa ku mubaka (Nabbi Muhammad) ow'ekitiibwa
  69,41,Ssi bigambo bya mutontomi naye Iman yammwe yentono
  69,42,Era sibigambo bya mulaguzi naye mufumitiriza kitono (nemutasobola ku byawula)
  69,43,Byassibwa ku ye okuva eri omulezi w'ebitonde
  69,44,Singa yetantala natwogeza ebigambo byetutaamutuma
  69,45,Twalimukutteko n'amanyi
  69,46,Olwo nno netumukutula omusuwa gw'obulamu
  69,47,Era tewali mumwe ayinza kutulemesa kutuukiriza ekyo kuye
  69,48,Mazima yyo Kur'ani kyakwebuulirira eri abatya Katonda
  69,49,Era mazima ddala tumanyi nti mu mmwe mulimu abalimbisa (Kur'ani)
  69,50,Mazima okugirimbisa (Kur'ani) kugenda kubeera kwejjusa kunene eri abakafiiri
  69,51,Mazima yo Kur'ani ge mazima aga namaddala
  69,52,Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama Katonda wo owekitiibwa
  70,1,"Mu ngeri y'okunyomerera\" omu ku bakafiiri\" yasaba oba ebibonerezo bijja bijje, so nga ate ddala byakujja"
  70,2,Bituuke ku bakafiiri tewali agenda kubigaana kubatuukako
  70,3,Nga biva eri Katonda nnyini madaala agalinya muggulu
  70,4,"Ba Malayika nga ne Jiburilu mwomutwalidde mwebayita nga bolekera eri Katonda, ekibatwalira olunaku lumu lwokka naye nga ate lwenkanankana e myaka e mitwalo etaano (egy'okunsi)"
  70,5,Kale nno gumikiriza olugumikiriza olulungi
  70,6,Mazima bbo balaba ebibonerezo nga biri wala
  70,7,Ate nga ffe tulaba nga biri kumpi
  70,8,Ku lunaku eggulu lwelirikulukuta nga omuzigo omusanuuse
  70,9,Ate ensozi neziba nga pamba asunsuddwa
  70,10,Era tewali wamukwano agenda kubuuza bikwata ku ffa nfe we
  70,11,"Bagenda kuba nga beeraba (naye nga tebayinza kuyambagana). Omwonoonyi olwokwagala okuwona ebibonerezo byolunaku olwo, aliyagala okwenunula nga awaayo abaanabe"
  70,12,Mukyalawe ne mugandawe
  70,13,N'ekika kye ekimukuuma
  70,14,"Nabantu bonna abali munsi, nga ekyo akikola awone ebibonerezo bya Katonda"
  70,15,"Tekigenda kuba nga bwayagala, mazima ayolekedde muliro ogubumbujja"
  70,16,Ogusiriiriza ddala eddiba
  70,17,Gugenda kukowoola buli eyakubayo amabega nakyuka okuva ku mazima
  70,18,"Era nga yakungaanyanga emmali nagitereka \"natagyamu mugabo gugitukuza"
  70,19,Mazima omuntu yatondebwa nga wamulugube
  70,20,Nga bwatuukibwako akabi ayitirira okutya
  70,21,Ate bwaba afunye akalungi ayitirira obukodo
  70,22,Okugyako abo abayimirizaawo e sswala
  70,23,Abo nga okusaala kwabwe kwalubeerera
  70,24,Era abo mu by'obugagga byabwe mulimu omugabo ogumanyiddwa
  70,25,Guweebwa abasabi n'abafuna mpola
  70,26,Era bebo abakakasa o kubeerawo kw'olunaku lw'enkomerero
  70,27,Era abo abatya ebibonerezo bya Mukama Katonda waabwe
  70,28,Kubanga mazima ebibonerezo byamukama Katonda sibyakuwonwa
  70,29,Era abo abakuuma obwerere bwabwe
  70,30,"Okugyako ku bakyala babwe oba abazaana abali mu mikono gyabwe, anti bo tebanenyezebwa kwabo"
  70,31,"Omuntu asukka ku abo, abo nno be babuusi bensalo"
  70,32,"Era abantu abalungi abogeddwako waggulu, bebatuukiriza obwesigwa bwabwe nendagaano zaabwe"
  70,33,Era abo abeesimbu mu bujulizi bwabwe
  70,34,Era abo abasaala e sswala zaabwe mu bujjuvu
  70,35,Abo nno balibeera mu jjana nga baweebwa ebitiibwa
  70,36,"Lwaki abakafiiri bajja gyoli nga banguwa \"so nga ate bakulimbisa"
  70,37,Nga bali ku mukono gwo ogwa ddyo ne ku mukono ogwa kkono mu bibinja
  70,38,Buli omu kubo asuubira okuyingira e jjana eyebyengera
  70,39,"Nedda sibwekiri, mazima ffe twabakola nga tubajja mwebyo byebamanyi"
  70,40,"Ndayira Katonda nannyini buvanjuba nobugwanjuba, mazima ffe tusobolera ddala"
  70,41,Okubawanyisaamu abalungi ababasinga era tetuli ffe baakulemesebwa
  70,42,"Ggwe baveeko babeere mu bukafiiri bwabwe nga bwebazannya okutuusa lwebalisisinkana olunaku lwabwe, olwo lwebalaganyisibwa"
  70,43,Olunaku lwebalifuluma mu ntaana zaabwe nga baduma nga balinga abagenda eri ebendera ebatereddwawo
  70,44,"Amaaso gabwe makakkamu, obuswavu nga bubabuutikidde, olwo lwe lunaku lwe balaganyisibwa"
  71,1,Mazima ffe twatuma Nuhu eri abantu be. Nti tiisa abantubo nga ebibonerezo abiruma ennyo tebinabajjira
  71,2,Naabagamba nti mazima nze ndi mutiisa omunnyonnyozi
  71,3,Nti musinze Katonda era mu mutye nange mungondere
  71,4,Olwo nno ajja kubasonyiwa ebyonoono byammwe (bye mwakola nga temunnaba kukkiriza mubaka era alyoke abawonye okuzikirira n'ebibonerezo ebibamalawo olumu). Abalindirize abatuuse ku ntuuko ze yabagerera. Mazima entuuko za Katonda bweziba zituuse tezirindirizibwa singa muba mumanyi
  71,5,"Awamu nekyo tebakkiriza\", Nuhu naagamba nti ayi Katonda wange nkowodde abantu bange ekiro n'emisana"
  71,6,Wabula okukowoola kwange tekubongedde okugyako okunnesamba
  71,7,"Mazima buli lwembadde mbakowoola badde eri okusonyiwa kwo bassa ennwe zaabwe mu matu gaabwe, ne beebikka engoye zaabwe, ne bakalambira era ne beekuluntaza olw'ekuluntaza"
  71,8,Ate era mazima mbakowodde mulwatu
  71,9,Era njogedde nabo mu lujjudde nga bwenjogedde nabo kinnomu
  71,10,Nembagamba nti mwegayirire Katonda wa mmwe anti mazima yye bulijjo musonyiyi
  71,11,Olwonno ajja kubatonnyeseza enkuba ey'omuddiringanwa
  71,12,Era abawe mu bungi emmaali n'abaana abawe n'amasamba abateeremu n'emigga
  71,13,Naye lwaki Katonda temumuwa kitiibwa
  71,14,Sso nga yabatonda ngabayisa mumitendera egyenjawulo
  71,15,Abaffe temulaba engeri Katondawo gyeyakolamu eggulu omusanvu nga myaliiro
  71,16,Nassaamu omwezi nga kitangaala nga bweyassamu enjuba nga eyaka
  71,17,Katonda yabatandika ng'abajja muttaka nemujja nga mukula nga ebimera bwe bikula
  71,18,Oluvanyuma abazza mu ttaka nga era bwagenda okubazuukiza alibagyemu bulambalamba (nga temuyise mu mitendera nga ebimera)
  71,19,Era Katonda yabateerawo ensi nga esoboka okuwangalirwako
  71,20,Mube nga musobola okutambulira muyo nga mukwata amakubo ge muba mwagadde
  71,21,"Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi mukama wange mazima ddala abantu abo banjemedde nebasalawo okugoberera oyo yenna emmaali ye n'abaana be bebitayongera okugyako okufafaganirwa"
  71,22,Nebakola olukwe sinziggu (bwebagezaako okutta Nuhu)
  71,23,Era nebagamba nti temugeza nemuva ku ba Katonda ba mmwe naddala Wadda ne Suwa'a ne Yagutha ne Yauka ne Nasira
  71,24,Olwekyo baabuza abantu bangi (Nange kyenva nkusaba nti) mukama Katonda abantu abeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako kubula
  71,25,Olwobwonoonyi bwabwe baazikiziribwa nebayingizibwa omuliro baali tebayinza kufuna abataasa yenna
  71,26,"Ye Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi Katonda wange toleka kunsi mukafiiri yenna"
  71,27,Anti singa obalekawo bajja kubuza abaddu bo era buli gwebanazaala ajja kuba mwononefu omukafiiri
  71,28,"Ayi Mukama Katonda wange nsonyiwa ne bakadde bange na buli yenna anaayingira mu nju yange kavuna anaaba nga mukkiriza, era nkusaba osonyiwe abakkiriza abasajja n'abakkiriza abakazi, wabula bo abeeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako okuzikirira"
  72,1,Bagambe ggwe Nabbi Muhammad nti nafuna obubaka nga waliwo amajinni agamu agaawuliriza nga nsoma Kur'ani negagamba nti mazima Kur'ani tugiwulidde nga yewuunyisa
  72,2,"Ekowoola oyo agiwuliriza okudda eri obulungamu era naffe tugikkirizza, era tetugenda kuddayo kugatta ku Katonda kintu kirala"
  72,3,"Era mazima ekitiibwa kya Mukama Katonda waffe kisukkulumu, tayinza kuba nti yeteerawo mukyala wadde omwana"
  72,4,Era mazima ddala ababuyabuya muffe baayogera nga ku Katonda ebigambo ebitemerere
  72,5,Era mazima ddala ffe twalowoozanga nti abantu na majjini baali tebayinza kwogera ku Katonda byabulimba
  72,6,Waliwo abantu abamu abaasabanga obuyambi okuva eri amajinni ekyagongera okuwaganyala
  72,7,Era mazima ddala amajinni gaalowooza nga bwemwalowooza nti Katonda yali tagenda kutuma mubaka yenna
  72,8,Era mazima ffe tubadde tugezaako okugenda ku ggulu netulisanga nga lijjudde abakuumi abakambwe nebitawuliro
  72,9,"Era mazima ffe waliwo enfo zetwatulangamu netuwuliriza ebifaayo, naye kati agezaako okuwuliriza asanga ebitawuliro nga bimuteeze"
  72,10,Wabula tetumanyi mu kukola ekyo kwali kulumya bitonde ebiri ku nsi oba Mukama Katonda wabyo yabyagaliza bulungamu
  72,11,Mazima nemuffe mulimu abalongoofu n'abatali era tuli ebibiina ebyenjawulo
  72,12,Era ffe tuli bakakafu nti tetuyinza kulemesa Katonda ku nsi era nga bwetutayinza kumulemesa ne tumuddukako
  72,13,"Era mazima ddala bwe twawulira obulungamu twabukkiriza, nga ate oyo yenna akkiriza Mukama Katonda we tayinza kutya butasasulwa oba okunyigirizibwa"
  72,14,"Mazima ddala muffe mulimu abasiramu nga bwemulimu abaabula. Oyo yenna asiramuka, abo nno bebaba banoonya amazima mu bwegendereza"
  72,15,Wabula bo abaabula be bagenda okubeera enku z'omuliro Jahannama
  72,16,Naye singa abantu banywerera ku kkubo ettuufu twalibawadde enkuba mu bungi
  72,17,"Tulyoke tubageseze ngeri ki gye be bazaamu e byengera, oyo yenna eyeesamba ebigambo bya Katondawe agenda kumubonereza n'ebibonerezo ebikambwe"
  72,18,"Mazima ddala emizigiti gya kusinzizamu Katonda yekka, kale nno temugatta ku Katonda ekintu kyonna"
  72,19,Era mazima ddala omuddu w'a Katonda (Nabbi Muhammad) bweyayimirira nga asaala amajinni gaasembera negamwetoloola kumpi kumwetuumako nga gali mu bibinja
  72,20,Bagambe (Gwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti mazima nze nsinza Katonda wange ate si mugattako kintu kirala kyonna
  72,21,(Ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) bagambe nti tekiri mu mikono gyange okubaggyirawo obuzibu obuba bubatuuseeko nga bwe kitali mu busobozi bwange okubafunira obulungamu
  72,22,Era bagambe nti mazima nze tewali muntu yenna ayinza kumponya bibonerezo bya Katonda singa mba mujeemedde. Era sisobola kufuna buddukiro nga si bwa Katonda
  72,23,"Nekiba nga ekisigadde kubatuusako bubaka obuva eri Katonda, naye abo bonna abajeemera Katonda n'omubakawe baakuyingira omuliro Jahannama, era nga b'akugubeeramu olubeerera"
  72,24,Okutuusizza ddala bwe balibanga balabye ebyo ebyabalagaanyisibwa olwo nno lwe bajja okukakasa nti ani alina omutaasa omunafu neggye ettono
  72,25,Bagambe ggwe Nabbi Muhammad nti mazima nze simanyi oba e bibonerezo bye mulaganyisibwa biri kumpi oba byakujja oluvanyuma lwebbanga eggwanvu
  72,26,"Ye yekka, Katonda yaamanyi ebitamanyiddwa ng'ate talina yenna gwabikkulira e byamabye"
  72,27,"Okugyako oyo gwaba alonze okubeera omubaka (kale nno oyo amubikkulira ebimu ku byamabye) era amuteerawo obukuumi bwa Malayika nga bamwetolodde, Sitani obutasobola kumutuukako"
  72,28,Nabbi alyoke amanye nti mazima ba Nabbi baatuukiriza obubaka bwa Katonda waabwe (nga naye bwa butuukiriza) era bamanye nti Katonda amanyi ebyo byonna bye bakola nga era bwamanyi buli kintu kyonna
  73,1,Owange ggwe eyeebikkirira (olwokutya okwakutuukako bwewafuna obubaka okuva ku Malayika Jiburilu omulundi ogwasoka)
  73,2,Golokoka osaale ekiro mpozzi lekayo akaseera katono
  73,3,Oyinza okusaala ekitundu kye kiro oba okukendezaako katono
  73,4,Oba oyinza okwongerako era bwoba osoma Kur'ani giwoomese
  73,5,Mazima ffe tujja kukutikka e kigambo ekizito
  73,6,Anti e sswala enzuukukire y'esinga okubuulirira omuntu (olw'okwerekereza otulo) era nga nebisomerwamu byebisinga okusomwa munsoma ennambulukufu
  73,7,Anti obudde obwemisana oleebukana nnyo (mu bintu ebirala)
  73,8,"Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama Katondawo, e kiseera kyonna okimuwe"
  73,9,"Mukama Katonda omufuziwo buvanjuba n'obugwanjuba tewali kirala kyonna kisaanye kusinzibwa okugyako yye, kale nno gwoba wesigamako"
  73,10,Era ogumikirize kw'ebyo bye boogera era obaveeko mu ngeri e nnungi
  73,11,"Naye ndekera abalimbisa, abagagga fugge, era balindirize akaseera katono"
  73,12,Mazima tulina empingu n'omuliro Jahiim
  73,13,N'ebyokulya ebitamirika n'ebibonerezo ebiruma
  73,14,Ebiribaawo ku lunaku e nsi n'ensozi lw'ebirikankana e nsozi ne zifuuka entuumo z'omusenyu ogufuumuka
  73,15,(Okuwona ebyo mukozese omukisa gwokuba nti) mazima ffe twabatumira omubaka nga yajja okubawaako obujulizi okufaananako nga bwe twatumira Firawo omubaka
  73,16,"Wabula Firawo yajeemera omubaka, kyetwava tumukwata olukwata olwamanyi"
  73,17,Kakati bwe mujeema muliwona mutya olunaku olulifuula abaana abato abakadde
  73,18,"Ate nga eggulu ligenda kuyulikamu olwebiribaawo ku lunaku olwo, nga ate Katonda kyalagaanyisa kiteekwa okutuukirira"
  73,19,"(Bwekiba nga bwekityo bwekiri), mazima ddala muteekwa mutwale Kur'ani nga kyakwebuulirira. N'olwekyo ayagala okuwona ateekeddwa okukwata ekkubo erimuzza eri Katonda we"
  73,20,"Mazima Katonda wo akimanyi nti oyimirira ekiro ng'osaala emirundi egimu kumpi bibiri byakusatu byekiro, oluusi kimu kyakubiri nga n'olundi kimu kyakusatu era nga naabamu ku bakkiriza abali naawe bwebatyo bwe bakola nga ate Katonda yaawa ebiragiro ebikola ekiro n'emisana, era nga amanyi nti temuyinza kumalayo kiro kyonna nga mukola Ibaada kye yava abawa ekisonyiwo, kale nno musome kyemuba musobodde mu Kur'ani nga musaala ekiro anti amanyi nti mu mmwe mulimu abalwadde nga n'abalala bagenda kubeera mu safari nga batambudde mu nsi olwokunoonya ebigabwa bya Katonda nga nabandi bagenda kubeera mu ntabaalo z'okuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda n'olwekyo musome ekyo kye muba musobodde mu Kur'ani nga musaala e sswala ya tahajjudi era muyimirizeewo e sswala eza faradha mutoole ne zzaka mu ngeri y'emu muwole Katonda oluwola olulungi nga muwaayo saddaaka. Akalungi konna kemweterekera mugenda ku kasanga mu maaso ga Katonda. Okukola ekyo kirungi era kyekirimu empeera ennene era musabe Katonda ekisonyiwo mazima Katonda musonyiyi oweekisa"
  74,1,Owange ggwe eyeebikiridde (olwokutya Malayika Jiburilu lwe yakuleetera obubaka okuva eri Katonda)
  74,2,Golokoka otiise abantu ebibonerezo bya Katonda
  74,3,Ne Mukama Katondawo yekka gwoba ogulumiza
  74,4,N'engoyezo zitukuze
  74,5,Amasanamu geewalire ddala
  74,6,Tokoleranga abantu obulungi ng'ogenderera kufunamu bulungi kuno ku nsi
  74,7,Beeranga mugumikiriza osobole okufuna okusiima kwa Mukama Katondawo
  74,8,Engombe bwerifuuyibwa (kulwokuzuukira)
  74,9,Olunaku olwo lugenda kuba lunaku luzito
  74,10,Terugenda kuba lwangu eri abakafiiri
  74,11,(Owange ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) ndeka nooyo gwe nnetondera
  74,12,Nemuwa ebyobugagga ebiyitirivu
  74,13,Nemuwa nabaana abatutumufu
  74,14,Ne mugaziyiriza olugaziya (e byenfuna obukulembeze n'ekitiibwa)
  74,15,Oluvanyuma alulunkanira okumwongera okusingako awo
  74,16,Nedda sijja kumwongera kuba yawakanya ebigambo byaffe (Kur'ani)
  74,17,Nja kumussaako e bibonerezo e bizito
  74,18,Anti mazima yye (Al Walid bin Mugiira) yalowooza era naasalawo okuvvoola Kur'ani
  74,19,Nakolimirwa okusinziira ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,20,Era ddala yakolimirwa ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,21,Oluvanyuma yakirowozaako
  74,22,Olwo nno ne yeekaba najja emitaafu
  74,23,Ne kyaddirira ebituufu yabivaako neyekuluntaza
  74,24,Olwo nno n'alangirira nti e bigambo bya Muhammad temuli wabula ddogo erijjibwa ku balogo abasooka
  74,25,Era byayogera tebisukka ku kuba bigambo bya muntu
  74,26,"(Katonda naagamba nti:) nja kumuyingiza omuliro Sakara"
  74,27,Naye omanyi Sakara kyeki
  74,28,Gwo muliro ogutagenda kulekawo kintu wadde okukitaliza
  74,29,Gwokera ddala negusiriiza eddiba lyomuntu
  74,30,Gukuumibwa ba Malayika kkumi na mwenda
  74,31,"Ate omulimu gwokukuuma omuliro tetwaguwa okugyako ba Malayika, era omuwendo gwabwe tetwaguteekawo okugyako nga kikemo eri abatakkiriza Katonda, so nga abo abaweebwa ekitabo ekyo kibongera kukakasa (ebyo bye baalina), ate bo abakkiriza (abagoberezi ba Nabbi Muhammad) kyongera kunyweza bukkiriza bwabwe, era abaweebwa ekitabo n'abakkiriza babe nga tebasigalamu kakunkuna, wabula nga (abanafunsi) abalina obulwadde mu mitima gyabwe n'abatakkiriza bagamba nti Katonda kiki kyagenderera mu kifananyi kino, bwatyo nno Katonda abuza nalungamya oyo gwaba ayagadde, ate tewali amanyi ggye lya Mukama Katondawo okugyako yye, ebyo byonna ebyogeddwa tewali kibigendererwamu okugyako okubuulirira omuntu"
  74,32,"Nedda (tekiri ng'abantu abamu bwe balowooza), mazima ndayidde omwezi"
  74,33,Ne ndayira n'ekiro mu kiseera we kiggwerako
  74,34,Ne ndayira n'amakya ngabusasaana
  74,35,Mazima ggwo (omuliro Sakara) kye kimu ku binene
  74,36,Ebyandibadde bibuulirira omuntu
  74,37,Eri oyo aba ayagadde mu mmwe okudda eri Katondawe oba okumwesamba
  74,38,Buli muntu agenda kubeera musingo gwa mirimugye
  74,39,Okugyako abo abalibeera ku mukono ogwaddyo
  74,40,Bagenda kubeera mu jjana nga babuuza ebifa
  74,41,Ku bonoonyi
  74,42,Nga babagamba nti ki ekibayingizza omuliro
  74,43,Baligamba nti tetubangako mu basaaze
  74,44,Era tetwaliisanga banaku
  74,45,Twabeeranga nabakubi bambekuulo
  74,46,Era twali tulimbisa olunaku lw'enkomerero
  74,47,Okutuusa okufa lw'ekwatutuukako
  74,48,Kale tebagenda kuganyulwa mu kuwolereza kwa bawolereza
  74,49,Kakano kiki ekibaddusa okuva ku kubuulirira kwa (Kur'ani kuno)
  74,50,Nga balinga entulege ezigobeddwa
  74,51,Ezidduka e mpologoma
  74,52,Wabula buli omu mubo ayagala aweebwe ebiwandiiko ebibikuddwa
  74,53,Nedda ekituufu kiri nti bbo tebakkiriza nkomerero
  74,54,Mazima ddala yo (Kur'ani) kyakubuulirira
  74,55,Oyo aba ayagadde yeebulirira nayo
  74,56,"Wabula tebayinza kwebuulirira okugyako nga Katonda ayagadde, yye ye nanyini kutiibwa era ye nanyini kusonyiwa"
  75,1,Tewali kingaana kulayira lunaku lwakuzuukira
  75,2,Era nga bwewatali kingaana kulayira omwoyo ogwejjusa
  75,3,Abaffe omuntu alowooza nti tetugenda kusobola kuzzaawo magumbage
  75,4,Nedda tukisobolera ddala nga bwetulisobola okuzzaawo ennwe zaabwe
  75,5,Wabula omuntu emirundi egisinga ayagala nnyo okuwangaalira mu kwonoona
  75,6,Ngabuuza (mu ngeri ey'okujerega n'okuwakanya) nti olunaku lwokuzuukira lulibaawo ddi
  75,7,Ddala lugenga kubaawo nga n'amaaso g'abantu galiralambala olwokutya
  75,8,Ekitangala kyomwezi kigenda kuggwawo
  75,9,Enjuba n'omwezi birigattibwa (nga tewakyasobola kubaawo kiro namisana)
  75,10,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kwebuuza nti nzirukirewa
  75,11,"Kyekyo ddala, tewagenda kubaawo muntu weyekweka"
  75,12,Obuddo ku lunaku olwo bujja kuba eri Mukama Katondawo
  75,13,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kutegeezebwa ebyo byonna byeyakola nebyataakola
  75,14,Wabula ate ddala omuntu ye yennyini amanyi bye yakola ne byataakola (newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayeetonda)
  75,15,Newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayetonda
  75,16,Bwoba osoma Kur'ani toyanguyiriza nga olowooza nti kyekinakuyamba okuginyweeza
  75,17,Anti okugikungaanya kuli kuffe nga era bwekiri kuffe okunywereza ku lulimi lwo ensoma ennungi
  75,18,Kale nno bwetumala okugikusomera (nga tugiyisa ku Jiburilu) goberera ensoma yaayo
  75,19,Era mazima okuginnyonnyola kuli kuffe
  75,20,(Ebyo ebyogeddwa waggulu bimala omuntu okwebuulirira nabyo) wabula ebyembi mmwe mwagala ebyokufuna byensi ebyamangu
  75,21,Nemuleka ebyolunaku lw’enkomerero
  75,22,Ebyenyi bya bantu abamu ku lunaku olwo bigenda kuba nga bitemagana
  75,23,Bigenda kutunula ku Mukama Katonda waabyo
  75,24,Ate nga ebyenyi bya bantu abalala bigenda kuba binyikaavu
  75,25,Nga bimanyidde ddala nti bigenda kutuukibwako akabi akanene akamenya nenkizi
  75,26,Naye omwoyo bwegutuuka mu ddokooli
  75,27,Abantu webagambira nti ani alina eddagala eriyinza okumuwonya
  75,28,Wabula yye ngamaze okukakasa nti agenda kufa
  75,29,Entumbwe ne yeegatta ku ntumbwe
  75,30,Olwo nno obuddo buba busigadde eri Katondawo
  75,31,Naye nga omufu teyasaddaaka wadde okusaala
  75,32,Wabula yalimbisa ebigambo bya Katonda nabyesamba
  75,33,Olwo nno naatambula nadda eri abantu be nga yeeraga
  75,34,(Aligambibwa nti ekyo) ekikutuuseeko kikugwanidde era ddala kikugwanidde (owange ggwe omwonoonyi)
  75,35,Ate era kikugwanidde ng'ate era ddala kikugwanidde
  75,36,Omuntu alowooza nti ayinza okulekwa neyeeyisa nga bwayagala
  75,37,Tajjukira nti yasooka kuba tondo lyamazzi agazaala agateekebwa mu nabaana
  75,38,"Oluvanyuma naafuuka ekisayisayi, olwo Katonda naamutonda namussaako byonna ebimufuula omuntu"
  75,39,"Nga bwatyo bwakola emitendera ebiri, omusajja n'omukazi"
  75,40,Abaffe oyo eyakola omuntu mu ngeri eyo tasobola kulamusa bafu
  76,1,Omuntu tajjukira nti waayitawo ekiseera kinene nga tayogerwako (nga tannatondebwa)
  76,2,Mazima ffe twatonda omuntu nga ava mu kwetabula kwamazzi (ag'omusajja n'omukazi) naye nga waakugezesebwa mu bulamu bwe. Kyetwava tumuwa okuwulira n'okulaba
  76,3,"Mazima ddala twamulaga e kkubo, kiri gyali yeebaza naasinza Katonda omu oba ajeema n'awakanya"
  76,4,Mazima ddala abakafiiri twabategekera enjegere n'amakoligo n'omuliro ogutuntumuka
  76,5,Mazima abakozi bobulungi bagenda kunywa ekyokunywa nga kitabuddwa mu kafuura
  76,6,"Olwo nno luliba luzzi abaddu b'a Katonda abeeyisa obulungi kwebagendanga okunywa, lugenda kukulukuta nga buli muntu lumutuukako waali"
  76,7,"(Bagenda kutuuka kwebyo kubanga) kuno ku nsi baatuukiriza nnaziri zaabwe, era nga batya olunaku olwo obuzibu bwalwo obugenda okubuutikira e nsi n'eggulu"
  76,8,Era bagabira abanaku ne bamulekwa nabasibe emmere awamu n'okuba nti bo bennyini bagyetaaga
  76,9,Nga bagamba nti mazima tubaliisa lwa Katonda tetubaagalamu mpeera wadde okwebaza
  76,10,(Ekitukozesa bino lwakuba nti) mazima ddala ffe tutya engeri gye tulisisinkanamu Katonda waffe ku lunaku e byenyi (bya bantu) lwe birijjula emitaafu nga byekabye
  76,11,N'olwekyo nno Katonda wakubawonya obuzibu bw'olunaku olwo era abawe okutangalijja kwe byenyi awamu n'essanyu
  76,12,"Era wakubasasula olwobugumikiriza, nga abayingiza e jjana omuli ebyambalo bya Siliki (awamu nokuba nti kunsi abasajja baaziyizibwa okumwambala)"
  76,13,"Balituula mu ntebe ez'omuwendo nga besigamye, tebagenda kutukwako kwokya kwanjuba wadde obutiti"
  76,14,"Era nga mulimu emiti egiribakolera ebisiikirize, era nga nebibala byamu bigenda kuba byangu byakunoga"
  76,15,Baligabulirwa ku sowane eza feeza era bakunywera ku girasi ezitemagana
  76,16,"Ziritemegana anti ziriba zaakolebwa mu feeza, ziriba zimala bumazi okubeeramu ekyokunywa ekimalawo obwetaavu bwoyo anywa"
  76,17,Era bagenda kuweebwa eby'okunywa ebiri mu girasi nga bitabulwamu entangawuzi
  76,18,"Eyo nno egenda kuba nsulo mu jjana eyitibwa \"Salsabiila"
  76,19,"Bagenda kuweerezebwanga abaweereza abolubeerera, nga bwobatunulako bwoti olaba lu'ulu asasanyiziddwa"
  76,20,Buli wonotunulanga mu jjana ng'olaba ebyengera ebisuffu n'obwanannyini obutaliiko kkomo
  76,21,"Baliba bambadde engoye eza Siliki omuweweevu owakiragala ne Siliki omuzito, era bagenda kuba bawundiddwa nebikomo ebya feeza, era Mukama Katonda waabwe agenda kubawa ebyokunywa ebitukuvu"
  76,22,"(Baligambwa nti) Mazima ebyo byonna yempeera yammwe, mazima okutegana kwa mmwe kusiimiddwa"
  76,23,Mazima ffe twakussaako Kur'ani (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) olussa
  76,24,"Kale nno beera mugumikiriza ku kugera kwa Katondawo, togezaako okugondera omwonoonyi oba omuwakanyi yenna"
  76,25,Era yogeranga kulinnya lya Mukama Katondawo enkya neggulo
  76,26,Ne mukiro muvunnamire ng'osaala era omutendereze mu ttumbi ebbanga ggwanvu
  76,27,"Mazima abatakkiriza basinga kwagala birungi byansi ebyamangu, ne basuulayo gwannaggamba ku bikwata ku lunaku lw'enkomerero oluzito"
  76,28,"Ffe twabatonda ne tugumya e biyungo byabwe, naye nga bwe tuba twagadde (tuyinza okubazikiriza) ne tuleeta abantu abalala"
  76,29,"Mazima obubaka bwa Kur'ani buno kya kwebulirira era nga kyakujjukiza, n'olwekyo aba ayagadde asanye y'eteerewo ekkubo erimutuusa eri Katondawe"
  76,30,"Naye ate temusobola kwagala okugyako nga Katonda ayagadde, mazima Katonda lubeerera amanyi, assa buli kintu mussa lyako"
  76,31,"Ayingiza oyo gwaba ayagadde mu kusaasirakwe, ate bbo abalyazamanyi yabategekera ebibonerezo ebiruma"
  77,1,Ndayidde empewo ekunta mu ngeri y'okugoberegana
  77,2,Era ndayidde kibuyaga akunta mu ngeri ey'amaanyi eyakabi
  77,3,Era ndayidde Malayika ezitambuza ebire olutambuza (olwokutonyesa enkuba)
  77,4,Era ndayidde Malayika ezikka okuva ewa Katonda nga zireeta ebyawula wakati w'amazima n'obulimba
  77,5,Era ndayidde Malayika ezireeta ebitabo n'obubaka eri ba Nabbi ba Katonda nga byakujjukiza
  77,6,Mu ngeri yokuba nti bijjawo ebyokwekwaasa oba nga byakutiisa
  77,7,Mazima bye mulaganyisibwa ebikwata ku lunaku lw'enkomerero n'okusasulwa bya kubaawo
  77,8,Emunyeenye lweziriggibwawo (newataba kitangaala kyaazo)
  77,9,Era eggulu bweririwumulwa (nerirabika nga emiryango)
  77,10,Era ensozi bwezirimerengulwa
  77,11,Era ababaka b'a Katonda bwebaliweebwa akadde k'okuwa obujulizi kwabo bebaatumwamu
  77,12,(Ebintu ebyo ebyentiisa) biribaawo ddi
  77,13,Bigenda kubaawo ku lunaku olwokusalawo n'okulamula wakati w'ebitonde
  77,14,Abaffe omanyi olunaku lw'okusalawo kyekki
  77,15,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kw'abo abalulimbisa
  77,16,Abaffe tetwazikiriza ababasokawo
  77,17,Netubagoberezaako abalala
  77,18,Bwetutyo nno bwetukola mu kubonereza abonoonyi
  77,19,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,20,Abaffe tetwabakola nga tubajja mu mazzi aganyomebwa
  77,21,Netugateeka mukifo ekigakuuma
  77,22,Okutuusa ebbanga eggere erimanyiddwa
  77,23,Bwetutyo nno bwetwateekateeka okutondebwa kwabwe tuli bateesiteesi abasinga obulungi
  77,24,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,25,Abaffe ensi tetwagikola nga ekungaanya
  77,26,Abalamu n'abafu (bonna ngabali muyo)
  77,27,Netugiteekamu e nsozi eziginyweza entumbiivu ne tubawa amazzi amalungi
  77,28,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,29,Ku lunaku lw'enkomerero abakafiiri baliragirwa nti mugende eri ebyo bye mwali mulimbisa
  77,30,Mugende eri ekisiikirize ekyomuliro ngakirimu ebitundu bisatu
  77,31,Wabula tebaliba na kibasiikiriza wadde e kibataasa nnimi z'amuliro
  77,32,Mazima omuliro ogwo gukasuka ebitawuliro nga biringa ebizimbe ebigulumivu
  77,33,Ebitawuliro ebyo nga biringa engamiya ez'akyenvu
  77,34,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,35,Olwo lunaku lwebatagenda kwogera
  77,36,Wadde okukkirizibwa okwetonda
  77,37,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,38,Luno lwe lunaku lw'okulamula tubakunganyizza mwenna n'aba bakulembera
  77,39,Bwe muba mulina engeri gyemuyinza okwebulankanyamu kale munnebulankanyeko
  77,40,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,41,Naye mazima abatya Katonda bagenda kubeera mu bisiikirize n'emigga egikulukuta
  77,42,N'ebibala byebaliba bagala
  77,43,Nga bagambibwa nti mulye era munywe nga mweyagala
  77,44,Mazima ffe bwetutyo bwetusasula abakozi b'obulungi
  77,45,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,46,"(Kuno ku nsi abakafiiri bagambwa nti) mulye, era mweyagale kitono, wabula mumanye nti muli bonoonyi (naye mukimanye nti waliyo enkomerero)"
  77,47,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,48,Bwebalagirwa okusaala tebasaala
  77,49,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,50,Olwo bigamboki ebitali Kur'ani byebagenda okukkiriza
  78,1,Beebuuzaganya ku ki
  78,2,Ku kigambo e kinene
  78,3,Ekigambo kye baawukaniramu ddala
  78,4,"Ekyo ssi bwekiri, bajja kumanya"
  78,5,Oluvanyuma nedda bajja kumanyira ddala
  78,6,Abaffe tetwabafuula e nsi e kyaliiro
  78,7,N’ensozi ne tuzifuula enkondo (eziginyweza obutayuuga)
  78,8,Ne tubatonda mu ngeri bbiri (omukazi n’omusajja)
  78,9,Ne tufuula okwebaka kwa mmwe nga kiwummulo
  78,10,Ne tufuula ekiro ekyambalo ekibabikka (olw’enzikiza yaakyo)
  78,11,Ne tufuula emisana omunoonyezebwa eky’okubabeezaawo
  78,12,Ne tuzimba waggulu wa mmwe emyaliiro emigumu musanvu
  78,13,Ne tuteekawo ettaala (enjuba) eyaka
  78,14,Ne tussa okuva mu bire by’enkuba amazzi agafukumuka
  78,15,Tulyoke tumeze nago empeke n’ebimera (ebirala)
  78,16,N’amalimiro amasaakaativu
  78,17,Mazima olunaku lw’okulamula lwaweebwa e kiseera e kigere
  78,18,Olwo Lwe lunaku e ngombe lw'erifuuyibwa ne mujja nga muli bibinja
  78,19,N’eggulu ne liggulwawo ne libeerako e miryango
  78,20,N’ensozi nezikungunsibwa ne ziba nga ezitabangawo
  78,21,Mazima omuliro Jahannama weeguli gulinze
  78,22,Nga bwe buddo bw’abo abamawaggali eri Katonda
  78,23,Baakugubeeramu byeya na byeya
  78,24,Nga bali mu gwo tebagenda kufuna buweerero wadde ak'okunywa akaweweeza
  78,25,Okugyako olweje n’amasira Ag'olusaayisaayi
  78,26,Nga y’empeera ebasaanira
  78,27,Kubanga baali tebasuubira nti walibayo okubalibwa
  78,28,Ne balimbisa nnyo ebigambo byaffe
  78,29,"So ng’ate buli kintu twakikuuma mu bujjuvu, mu buwandiike"
  78,30,Kale mukombe ku kibabu ky'ebikolwa byammwe kubanga tetujja kubongera okugyako ebibonerezo
  78,31,Mazima abatya Katonda bajja kufuna okwesiima (okulimu buli kyonna kye baagala)
  78,32,Amalimiro n’emizabbibu
  78,33,N’abawala ab’amabeere amatutu
  78,34,N’amagiraasi agajjudde eby’okunywa
  78,35,Nga bali mu yo (e jjana) tebagenda kuwulira bigambo bya butaliimu wadde eby’obulimba
  78,36,"Nga y’empeera okuva eri omulezi wo, nga kuweebwa okumatiza"
  78,37,"Oyo nanyini Ggulu omusanvu n’ensi n’ebiri wakati wa byombi, oweekisa ekingi, tebalyetantala kwogeraganya naye"
  78,38,"Jiburilu ne ba malayika abalala ku lunaku lwe baliyimirira nga bali mu nnyiriri nga bonna tewali ayogera okugyako oyo yekka Katonda omusaasizi, gw’aliba akkiriza okwogera ate n'ayogera bituufu"
  78,39,Olwo lwe lunaku olw’amazima. Omuntu ayagala emirembe alwetegekere afune obuddo eri Katonda we
  78,40,"Mazima tubatiisizza ebibonerezo ebiri okumpi ennyo. Olunaku omuntu lw’aliraba ebyo emikono gye bye gyakola. Ku lunaku olwo omukaafiiri aligamba: ye nga zinsanze, singa nfuuse ettaka"
  79,1,Ndayira Malayika ezisikambula emyoyo gy’abajeemu mu bukambwe
  79,2,Era ndayira Malayika ezisowola emyoyo gy’abakkiriza obusowozi
  79,3,Era ndayira Malayika eziwugira mu bbanga oluwuga
  79,4,Era ndayira Malayika ezivuganya oluvuganya nga zitwala emyoyo gy’abakkiriza mu jjana
  79,5,Ne ndayira ne Malayika ezissa mu nkola ebiragiro (Byange)
  79,6,(Mukimanye nti ebitonde byonna bigenda kuzikirira) ku lunaku buli kintu kyonna lwe kirikankana nga engombe efuuyiddwa
  79,7,Luligobererwa olufuuwa olw'okubiri (olw'okuzuukira)
  79,8,E mitima gy’abatakkiriza ku lunaku olwo giribeera mu kutya
  79,9,Amaaso gaabwe nga makkakkamu
  79,10,"Bagamba (nga bajerega), nti \"Mazima ddala tulizzibwawo mu bulamu nga bwetulimu kati"
  79,11,Bwe tuliba tumaze okufuuka amagumba amamerengufu
  79,12,Bongerako ne bagamba nti (okwonno bwekiriba bwekityo) kuliba kudda kwa kufaafaaganirwa
  79,13,Mazima okuzuukira lugenda kubeera olukanga lumu lwokka
  79,14,Baligenda okulaba nga bali ku ngulu ku nsi
  79,15,Abaffe wamanya ku kyafaayo kya Nabbi Musa
  79,16,Awo Katonda we yakoowoolera Musa nga (Musa) ali mu lusenyi olutukuvu 'Tuwa
  79,17,N'amugamba nti genda eri Firaawo kubanga ye asusse mu bujeemu ne mu buwakanyi
  79,18,"Omugambe nti, Abaffe waalyetaaze okwetukuza (n'okkiriza mukama Katonda wo)"
  79,19,Ndyoke mbe nga nkulungamya eri Katonda wo obeere nga omutya
  79,20,(Nabbi Musa) n’alaga Firaawo obujulizi obwenkukunala
  79,21,(Firaawo) naalimbisa era n’ajeema
  79,22,Bwe yamala n'abikuba amabega era n’akola kaweefube w'okubirwanyisa
  79,23,"N’akungaanya (amagye ge, abakungu be, n’abalogo) n’alangirira"
  79,24,Ng’agamba nti nze Katonda wa mmwe owa waggulu
  79,25,Katonda n’amubonereza n’okumuzikiriza olw’ekisobyo ekyasembayo n’ekyasooka
  79,26,Mazima mu ekyo (eky’okuzikiriza Firaawo) mulimu eky’okulabirako eri oyo atya Katonda
  79,27,"Abaffe, mmwe be mweraba mwe musinga obuzibu okutonda okusinga e ggulu? Yalitonda nno"
  79,28,(Awamu n'obugevvu bwalyo) yaliwanika n'alitereeza
  79,29,Aleeta enzikiza yaalyo n’aggyayo ekitangaala kyalyo
  79,30,N’ensi oluvanyuma lwebyo yagyaliira
  79,31,Muyo mwennyini mweyajja amazzi gaayo namalundiro gaayo
  79,32,N’ensozi yazisimba n'azinyweeza
  79,33,(Ebyo yabikola) lwa kugasa mmwe n'ensolo za mmwe
  79,34,Akabenje akanene bwe kalijja (olwo lwe luliba olunaku lw'enkomerero)
  79,35,Olunaku lw’alijjukira omuntu ebyo byonna bye yakola
  79,36,Omuliro Jahiimu negulagibwa eri yenna alaba
  79,37,Oyo yenna eyasukka mu kujeema
  79,38,N’asukkulumya obulamu bw’ensi (ku bw'enkomerero)
  79,39,Mazima omuliro Jahiimu bwe buddo bwe
  79,40,Oyo aliba nga yatya okuyimirira mu maaso ga Mukama we (Katonda). N’aziyiza omwoyo gwe ku by’obwagazi
  79,41,"Mazima e jjana, bwe buddo bwe"
  79,42,"Bakubuuza gwe (Nabbi Muhammad) ebikwata ku lunaku lw’enkomerero, nti lulibaawo ddi"
  79,43,Wa gy'onoggya okulwogerako
  79,44,Omulezi wo Katonda yekka ya manyi ebirukwatako
  79,45,Mazima ggwe oli mutiisa eri oyo alutya
  79,46,Mazima bwe baliraba olunaku olwo balibanga abataatuula ku nsi okugyako ekiseera ky'olweggulo oba e kye nkya
  80,1,"(Nabbi Muhammad) azze emitaafu, n’akubayo amabega"
  80,2,Muzibe bw’amujjidde
  80,3,Ki ki ekikumanyisa ob'olyawo (muzibe oyo) aneetukuza
  80,4,Oba anaabuulirirwa okubuulira nekumugasa
  80,5,Oyo eyeegaggawaza nga yeematira
  80,6,Ate ggwe gwe weemalira
  80,7,Bw’ateetukuza kiki ekinaakubaako
  80,8,So ng’oyo akujjidde ng’ayanguwa
  80,9,Era ng’atya Katonda
  80,10,Ate ggwe gw’otofaako
  80,11,"Nedda si bwe kyandibadde, mazima yyo (Kur'ani) kya kwe buulirira"
  80,12,Aba ayagadde yeebuulirira nayo
  80,13,Eri mu biwandiiko eby’ekitiibwa ennyo
  80,14,"Ebigulumizibwa, ebitukuvu"
  80,15,Ebiri mu mikono gya Ba Malayika abawandiisi
  80,16,"Ab'ebitiibwa, abatukuvu"
  80,17,"Omuntu yakolimirwa, ki ki ddala ekimuwakanyisa Katonda"
  80,18,(Omuntu talaba) kintu ki Katonda mwe yamutonda
  80,19,Mu mazzi (e nkwaso) mwe yamutonda n'amugerera (byonna ebiri mutuukako)
  80,20,Oluvanyuma n’amwanguyiza ekkubo ly’okuzaalibwa
  80,21,Bw’amala n’amutta era n’aziikibwa mu kabbuli
  80,22,Oluvanyuma alimuzuukiza bwaliba ayagadde
  80,23,Wabula omuntu tatuukiriza ebyo Katonda by’amulagira okukola
  80,24,Omuntu ateekwa atunuulire by’alya (emitendera gye biyitamu)
  80,25,Mazima ffe tufuukirira amazzi olufukirira (olusaanidde)
  80,26,Ne tulyoka twasa ettaka olwasa (olusaanira ebimera)
  80,27,Olwo nno ne tumeza mu lyo e mpeke
  80,28,E mizabbibu n’ebimera e bizimba omubiri
  80,29,N’emizayituni n’emitende
  80,30,N’ennimiro ezisaakaatiddemu (e miti emiwanvu)
  80,31,N’ebibala n’omuddo oguliibwako e bisolo
  80,32,Bibagase n’ebisolo bya mmwe
  80,33,Naye okuboggola bwe kuliba kuzze
  80,34,Olunaku omuntu lwalidduka mugandawe
  80,35,"Ne maamawe, ne kitaawe"
  80,36,"Ne mukyalawe, n’abaanabe"
  80,37,Buli muntu ku lunaku olwo ajja kuba ku nsonga emukwatako yekka
  80,38,Ebyenyi ebimu ku lunaku olwo bigenda kuba byakaayakana
  80,39,"Nga biriko akamwenyumwenyu, nga bisanyufu"
  80,40,Ate ebyenyi ebirala bigenda kuba nga bigubye
  80,41,Nga ekizikiza kibibisse
  80,42,"Abo nno be baawakanya Katonda, aboonoonyi"
  81,1,Enjuba bw'erizingwako
  81,2,Nga n’emunyeenye zikunkumuse
  81,3,Era ensozi bwe zirikungunsibwa (ne zigibbwawo)
  81,4,Nga n’ebisolo ebyo mu maka nga tebikyafiibwako (newakubadde nga biriba mawako)
  81,5,N’ebisolo by’omu nsiko nabyo nga bikungaanyiziddwa
  81,6,Nga n’ennyanja zikuumiddwako omuliro (ne zibumbujja)
  81,7,"Nga n’emyoyo gigatiddwa buli egifaanagana nga giri wamu (Emirungi nga giri n’emirungi, e mibi nga giri n’emibi)"
  81,8,Era omwana omuwala eyaziikibwa nga mulamu bw'aliba abuuziddwa
  81,9,Kibi ki ekyamussa
  81,10,"Ebiwandiiko bwe biribeera nga bisasaanyiziddwa (nga buli kiwandiiko kituuka ku nnannyini kyo, omuli ebyo bye yakola ku nsi)"
  81,11,E ggulu bwe liriba liggyiddwawo
  81,12,Nga n’omuliro gukoleezeddwa
  81,13,Nga n’ejjana esembezeddwa
  81,14,Olwo omuntu alimanya ekyo kye yakola (kibe kirungi oba kibi)
  81,15,Ndayira e munyeenye ezibulawo
  81,16,Ezibula emisana ne zirabika ekiro
  81,17,Era ndayira ekiro bwe kiba nga kyolekedde okuggwaawo
  81,18,Era ndayira n’amakya g’obudde nga busaasaana
  81,19,Mazima yyo (Kur'ani) kigambo kya mubaka (Jiburilu) ow'ekitiibwa (ky’aggya eri Katonda n’akireetera Nabbi Muhammad)
  81,20,Oyo (Jiburilu) owaamaanyi era ow'ekitiibwa eri nnannyini Arishi
  81,21,Agonderwa (ba Malayika banne) eyo (mu ggulu) ng'ate mwesigwa
  81,22,Era munnammwe (Nabbi Muhammad) si mulalu
  81,23,Mazima ddala ye (Muhammad) yamulaba (Jiburilu) mu bweyolefu nga ajjudde obwengula
  81,24,Era tali (Nabbi Muhammad) ku bigambo ebyekwese (ebikwata ku bubaka obuva eri Katonda n'ebigambo by'omu ggulu) ayinza obutatuukiriza
  81,25,(Ebigambo bya Kur'ani Muhammad byayogera) si bigambo bya sitaani omukolimire
  81,26,Naye ddala mulaga wa
  81,27,Wabula Yo (Kur'ani) kyakubuulirira eri ebitonde byonna
  81,28,Eri oyo mu mmwe aba ayagadde okulungama
  81,29,Naye ate temujja kwagala okugyako nga Katonda Omulezi w’ebitonde ayagadde
  82,1,E ggulu bwe ririba lyeyasizzaamu
  82,2,N'emunyenye bwe ziriba nga zivudde waggulu ne zisaasaana
  82,3,N'ennyanja bwe ziriba nga ziwaguludde
  82,4,Ne Kabbuli bwe ziriba nga zifuukuddwa (abafu bonna ne bavaayo)
  82,5,Omuntu alimanya ebyo bye yakulembeza okukola ne bye yasembyayo
  82,6,Owange ggwe omuntu kale kiki ekyakugayaaza okukuggya ku muleziwo (Katonda) Omugabi
  82,7,Oyo eyakutonda n’akutereeza era n’akwenkanyankanya
  82,8,Mu kifaananyi kyonna kye yayagala mwe yakutondera
  82,9,"Nedda, wabula mulimbisa olunaku olw’okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)"
  82,10,Mazima muliko abakuumi (Ba Malayika)
  82,11,Abeekitiibwa abawandiisi (abawandiika ebyo byonna ebikolebwa)
  82,12,Bamanyi ebyo byonna byemukola
  82,13,Mazima abakozi b’obulungi balibeera mu byengera
  82,14,Era mazima abakozi b’ebibi bagenda kubeera mu muliro oguyitibwa Jahiimu
  82,15,Bagenda kuguyingira ku lunaku olw’okusasulwa (olw'enkomerero)
  82,16,Tebagenda ku gwebulankanyako
  82,17,On'omanyira ku ki olunaku olw'okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)
  82,18,Naye ddala on'omanyira ku ki olunaku olwokusasulwa (Katonda yakiddamu olwokuggumiza obukulu bw’olunaku olwo)
  82,19,Olunaku omwoyo lwe gutaliba na buyinza bugasa mwoyo mulala na kintu kyonna. N’ebiragiro ku lunaku olwo biriba bya Katonda yekka
  83,1,Okuzikirira kuli ku abo abakendeeza ebipimo
  83,2,"Abo bwe baba nga beebapimirwa, basaba ebipimo byabwe bijjuzibwe"
  83,3,"So nga bwe baba nga be balengera abalala, oba be bapima, bakendeeza (ebipimo)"
  83,4,Abaffe tebakakasa nti mazima ddala baakuzuukizibwa
  83,5,Ku lunaku oluzito (olw'enkomerero)
  83,6,Olunaku abantu lwe baliyimirira mu maaso g'omulezi w’ebitonde
  83,7,Mazima ddala ebiwandiiko by’emirimu gy’aboonoonyi biri mu Sijjiin
  83,8,Naye omanyi Sijjiin kye ki
  83,9,Ky’ekitabo ekiwandiikibwamu ebibi by’omuntu
  83,10,"Okuzikirira ku lunaku olwo, kulibeera ku abo abalimbisa"
  83,11,Abo abalimbisa olunaku lw’okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)
  83,12,Tewali alimbisa lunaku olwo okugyako oyo asukka ensalo z’amateeka ga Katonda era omwonoonyi
  83,13,Bw’aba asomeddwa ebigambo byaffe (Kur'ani) agamba nti ebyo nfumo z’abaasooka
  83,14,"Nedda, ssi bwekiri; wabula bye baali bakola byetuuma ku mitima gyabwe"
  83,15,Mazima ddala abatakkiriza ku lunaku olwo baakuziyizibwa okulaba Omulezi waabwe (Katonda)
  83,16,Mazima ddala baakuyingira omuliro Jahiimu
  83,17,Oluvanyuma bagenda kugambibwa nti ekyo kye mwalimbisanga
  83,18,Mazima ddala ebiwandiiko by’abakozi b’obulungi biri mu Illiyyiina
  83,19,Naye omanyi Illiyyiina kye ki
  83,20,Ky’ekitabo ekiwandiikibwamu ebirungi by’omuntu
  83,21,Bakisemberera Ba malayika abali okumpi ne Katonda
  83,22,Mazima abakozi b’obulungi bagenda kubeera mu byengera
  83,23,Nga bali ku bitanda ebiwunde nga batunuulira ebintu ebibeetoolodde
  83,24,Essanyu eriribeera ku maaso gaabwe ligenda ku kulaga okwesiima kwe balibaamu
  83,25,Baligabulwanga omubisi (ogw’omu jjana) omusaanikire obulungi
  83,26,"(Olunaagunywangako) ng'owulira akawoowo ka misk. Ne mu kyo, abaagala okuvuganya mu kukola emirimu emirungi bavuganye"
  83,27,Omubisi ogwo gugenda kutabulwa mu Tasnim
  83,28,Tasnim nsulo erinywebwangako abalibeera okumpi ne Katonda
  83,29,Mazima abantu abo abaali abajeemu baalinga ku nsi nga basekerera abakkiriza
  83,30,Bwe baabayitangako nga babageyesa amaaso
  83,31,Ate nga bwe baddanga mu bantu baabwe nga beewaana
  83,32,Bwe baabalabangako nga bagamba nti mazima abo baabulira ddala
  83,33,Naye tebatumwanga kubeera nga bebalondoola emirimu gya bali
  83,34,Wabula olwaleero (olunaku lw'enkomerero) abo abakkiriza bajja kubeera nga basekerera abatakkiriza
  83,35,(Abakkiriza) nga bali ku bitanda ebiwunde nga babakeneka
  83,36,(Nga bwe bagamba nti) abaffe abatakkiriza basasuddwa bye baalinga bakola
  84,1,Eggulu bwe liryeyasaamu
  84,2,"Ne ligondera ekiragiro kya Mukama waalyo, era nga bwe kyandibadde"
  84,3,Ensi bw'eriseeteezebwa
  84,4,N'ewandula ebigirimu n'esigala nga njereere
  84,5,N'egondera ekiragiro kya mukama waayo era nga bwe kyandibadde
  84,6,Owange ggwe omuntu! Otakabana olutakabana (okukola e mirimu) ng'odda eri Katondawo. Era oli wakumusisinkana
  84,7,Kale nno omuntu aliweebwa ekitabokye mu mukonogwe ogwa ddyo
  84,8,Agenda kubalwa olubala olwangu
  84,9,Era adde eri banne nga musanyufu
  84,10,Naye oyo aliweebwa ekitabokye e mabega w'omugongogwe
  84,11,Agenda kukuba e biwoobe
  84,12,Yeesogge omuliro Sa-iira
  84,13,Kubanga yabeeranga (ku nsi) mu bantube nga musanyufu (mu kujeemera amateeka ga Mukama Katonda)
  84,14,Bambi! yalowooza nti tagenda kuzuukira
  84,15,"So nno, mazima Katondawe yalinga amulaba"
  84,16,Ndayira ekire ekimyufu (ekibaawo ng'enjuba yakagwa)
  84,17,Ne ndayira n'ekiro n'ebyo bye kikungaanya
  84,18,Era ndayira omwezi bwe guba gujjudde
  84,19,Mujja kukyusibwakyusibwa (mu mbeera za mmwe nga muva mu mbeera okudda ku ndala)
  84,20,Naye lwaki tebakkiriza
  84,21,Ne Kur'ani bwe basomerwa tebavunnama
  84,22,Wabula e nsonga ebagaana okuvunnama lwakuba nti abakafuuru balimbisa (Kur'ani)
  84,23,So nga Katonda amannyidde ddala bye bakweka (mu mitima gyabwe)
  84,24,Bawe amawulire nti bagenda kubeera mu bibonerezo ebiruma
  84,25,Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirongoofu. Abo be bagenda okufuna e mpeera etakutukawo
  85,1,Ndayira e ggulu eririmu ebifo omutambulira e munyeenye (nga mwe muli e njuba n’omwezi)
  85,2,Era ndayira olunaku olwalagaanyisibwa (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  85,3,Era ndayira oyo aliwa obujulizi n’oyo gwe balibuwaako (ku lunaku lw’enkomerero)
  85,4,Katonda yagoba mu kusaasirakwe abo abaasima agannya
  85,5,Gebaakumamu omuliro ogubumbujja
  85,6,Bwe baatuula awo ku mabbali waagwo
  85,7,Nga bo (bennyini) balaba buli kyonna kyebakola ku bakkiriza
  85,8,Tebaalina kye baali babavunaana okugyako okukkiriza Katonda oweekitiibwa atenderezebwa
  85,9,"Oyo, obufuzi bwe ggulu omusanvu n'ensi bwonna bubwe. Era Katonda alaba buli kintu"
  85,10,"Mazima abo abaawalagganya abakkiriza abasajja n’abakkiriza abakazi ate ne bateenenya, bakutuukibwako e bibonerezo by’omuliro Jahannama era balina e bibonerezo by’omuliro ogwokya ennyo"
  85,11,Mazima abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi bajja kufuna e jjana nga mukulukutira muyo emigga. Okwo nno kwe kwesiima okwannamaddala
  85,12,Mazima okukwata kwa Mukamaawo kwamaanyi nnyo
  85,13,Kubanga yye ye mutandisi wa buli kintu era yewookubizzaawo
  85,14,"Era musonyiyi nnyo, era abaagala nnyo"
  85,15,"Yye ye nannyini Arishi, Oweekitiibwa"
  85,16,Akola buli ky’aba ayagadde
  85,17,Wali owulidde ku byafaayo by’amagye
  85,18,Aga Firawo n’abantu ba Thamuud
  85,19,Wabula abo abatakkiriza bali mu kulimbisa
  85,20,So nga Katonda abeetoolodde
  85,21,Wabula yo Kur'ani (eyassibwa ku Nabbi Muhammad) ya kitiibwa
  85,22,Eri mu ggwandiikiro erikuumwa obutiribiri
  86,1,Ndayira e ggulu ne munyeenye ezirabika e kiro
  86,2,Naye omanyi e munyeenye ezirabika ekiro kye ki
  86,3,Z’emunyeenye ezaaka ennyo ekitangaala kyazo ne kiyita mu nzikiza ne kituuka ku nsi
  86,4,Buli muntu yenna aliko abakuumi (Ba Malayika)
  86,5,Kale nno omuntu yalibadde atunuulira kye yatondebwamu
  86,6,Yatondebwa ng’aggyibwa mu mazzi agasambattuka
  86,7,Nga gava wakati w’omugongo gw'omusajja n’amasaabiro g'omukazi
  86,8,Mazima ddala oyo (Katonda) asobolera ddala okumuzzaawo
  86,9,Ku lunaku ebyama byonna lwe biribikkulwa
  86,10,Omuntu tagenda kuba na maanyi gonna yadde omutaasa
  86,11,Era ndayira e ggulu ewava e nkuba etonnya nga e ddingana
  86,12,Ne ndayira n’ettaka eryeyasa olw’okumeza e bimera
  86,13,Mazima ddala yo (Kur'ani) kigambo ekyawula wakati w’amazima n’obulimba
  86,14,Kur'ani si ya lusaago
  86,15,Mazima abatakkiriza basala e nkwe
  86,16,Nange nenkola enteekateeka (zange)
  86,17,"Abatakkiriza balindirize, nange mbawadde akaseera katono"
  87,1,Tendereza erinnya ly’omulabiriziwo owa waggulu
  87,2,Oyo eyatonda n'atereeza
  87,3,Era eyateekateeka buli kintu n'akyenkanyankanya
  87,4,Era oyo ameza omuddo oguliibwa e bisolo
  87,5,Oluvanyuma agufuula omukalu
  87,6,Tujja kukusomesa (Kur'ani) obeere nga teweerabira
  87,7,Okugyako ebyo Katonda by’anaaba ayagadde okukwerabiza. Katonda y’amanyi ebyogerwa mu lwatu ne mu kyama
  87,8,Tujja kukwanguyiza amateeka gabeere mangu
  87,9,"Kale buulirira, okubuulirira bwe kuba nga kunaagasa"
  87,10,Anaaganyulwa oyo atya Katonda
  87,11,Omwonoonyi ajja ku kwesamba (okubuulirira okwo)
  87,12,Oyo alyesogga omuliro ogwamaanyi
  87,13,"Ng’amaze (okusonsekebwa mu muliro ogwo), tagenda kufa wadde okufuna obulamu (obwesiimisa)"
  87,14,Mazima yeesiimye omuntu e yeetukuza
  87,15,N’ayogera ku linnya ly’omuleziwe olwo nno n’asaala
  87,16,Wabula mmwe musukkulumya obulamu obw’ensi
  87,17,So nga obulamu obw'enkomerero bwe businga obulungi era bwe bwo kusigalawo
  87,18,Mazima bino biri mu biwandiiko ebyasooka
  87,19,Ebiwandiiko bya Ibrahim ne Musa
  88,1,Abaffe wali ofunye okunyumizibwa ku kibuutikira (eky’olunaku lw'enkomerero)
  88,2,Olunaku olwo ebyenyi bigenda kuba nga biswavu
  88,3,"Nga bitawaana, nga bikoowu"
  88,4,Nga byesonseka omuliro ogwengeredde
  88,5,Bigenda kunywesebwa ku luzzi olweseze
  88,6,(Abantu abo) tebagenda kubeera na kya kulya kyonna okugyako e miti egy’amaggwa
  88,7,Egitaliimu kiriisa wadde okuwonya e njala
  88,8,Ebyenyi e birala bigenda kubeera mu byengera
  88,9,Bigenda kusiima olw’okutakabana kwa byo
  88,10,Nga biri mu jjana ey’awaggulu
  88,11,Togenda kuwulira mu yo bigambo bya butaliimu
  88,12,Mu jjana mulimu e nsulo e zikulukuta
  88,13,Era nga mulimu ebitanda ebisitufu (Ebiwunde)
  88,14,N’ebikopo ebinywerwamu ebitegekeddwa
  88,15,N’emitto egisimbiddwa ennyiriri
  88,16,N’ebyaliiro nga byanjuluziddwa
  88,17,Abaffe tebatunuulira (olutunuulira olw’okuyiga) engamiya ngeri ki bwe yatondebwa
  88,18,N’eggulu nga bwe lyasitulwa
  88,19,N’ensozi engeri gye zaasimbwamu
  88,20,N’ensi engeri gye yaseetezebwamu
  88,21,Kale nno buulirira gwe (Nabbi Muhammad) kubanga oli mubuulirizi
  88,22,Toliiwo kubakaka
  88,23,Naye abo abanaava ku bigambobyo ne bajeema
  88,24,Katonda agenda okubabonereza e bibonerezo e bisinga okuba e bikakali
  88,25,Mazima ddala gyetuli y’eri obuddo bwabwe
  88,26,Oluvanyuma ddala okubalibwa kwabwe kuli ku ffe
  89,1,Ndayira e mambya
  89,2,N’ebiro e kkumi
  89,3,N’ebibiri bibiri n’ebyensusuuba
  89,4,N’ekiro bwekiba nga kitambula (nga kijja oba nga kivaawo)
  89,5,Abaffe mu kulayira kuno temuliimu kwebuulirira eri oyo alina amagezi
  89,6,Tewamanya ebyo Omuleziwo (Katonda) bye yatuusa ku bantu b'ekika kya A'adi
  89,7,Aba-Irama abawagguufu
  89,8,Tewatondebwangayo babafaanana mu nsi
  89,9,N’ebyo bye yatuusa ku ba Thamuud abaawukuulanga e njazi mu lusenyi
  89,10,N'ebyo bye yatuusa ku Firaawo nannyini nkondo
  89,11,Abo bonna (aboogeddwako) beewaggula kuno ku nsi
  89,12,Ne bayitiriza nnyo obwonoonefu
  89,13,Omuleziwo (Katonda) kye yava abafukirira e bibonerezo e by'enjawulo
  89,14,Mazima ddala Omuleziwo (Katonda) abalindiridde
  89,15,"Wabula omuntu, Omuleziwe (Katonda) bw'amugezesa n'amugabira e birungi, omuntu oyo agamba nti Katonda wange ampadde"
  89,16,Ku ludda olulala bw'aba amugezesezza n'amufundiza ebyenfunaye agamba nti omulezi wange (Katonda) anzikakkanyiza
  89,17,"Nedda, wabula temuyisa bulungi ba Mulekwa"
  89,18,Era temwekubiriza kuliisa banaku
  89,19,"Ate nga mulya emmaali ya ba Mulekwa, olulya olugimalawo"
  89,20,Era nga mwagala eby'enfuna okwagala okuyitiridde
  89,21,"Nedda eyo si y'endaba e ntuufu ey’ebintu, e nsi bwe ribeera nga ebetenteddwa"
  89,22,Omuleziwo n'ajja nga ne Ba Malayika basimbye ennyiriri
  89,23,"Era kwolwo o muliro Jahannama gulireetebwa, kwolwo nno omuntu alijjukira (bye yakola ku nsi) naye okujjukira kuno kugenda ku mugasaaki"
  89,24,"Agenda kugamba: zinsanze nze. Singa nategekera obulamu bwange buno"
  89,25,Olunaku olwo (Katonda) e bibonerezo by'agenda okubonereza nabyo tewali n'omu yali abibonerezzaako
  89,26,Era ensiba gyalisiba ku lunaku olwo tewali yali agisibyeko
  89,27,Owange ggwe omwoyo omutebenkevu (omuntu)
  89,28,Dda eri Omuleziwo ng'oli musanyufu era asiimiddwa
  89,29,Olwo nno oyingire mu baddu bange (abalongoofu)
  89,30,Era oyingire mu jjana yange
  90,1,Ndayira ekibuga kino (Makkah)
  90,2,Nga naawe (Muhammad) oli mutuuze mu kibuga kino
  90,3,Era ndayira omuzadde ne baazaala
  90,4,Mazima twakola omuntu nga lubeerera abeera mu kutawaana
  90,5,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu ayinza ku musobola
  90,6,Ng’agamba nti nsaasanyiza emmaali nyingi nnyo
  90,7,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu amulaba
  90,8,Tetwamuwa amaaso abiri
  90,9,N’olulimi n’emimwa ebiri
  90,10,Era ne tumulungamya okumanya amakubo abiri (ery'ekirungi n'ery'ekibi)
  90,11,Kale singa yabikozesa mu kuvvuunuka obizibu (bw'olunaku lw'enkomerero n'aba nga akozesa bye yafuna naafunamu e nkomerero)
  90,12,Abaffe obuzibu obumanyi (n'ekiyinza okubukuyambako)
  90,13,Kuta muddu
  90,14,Oba okuliisa mu kiseera eky’enjala
  90,15,"Mulekwa, owooluganda olw’okumpi"
  90,16,Oba omwavu lunkupe
  90,17,Ate era n’abeera mu abo abakkiriza. Ng’era balaamiragana obugumiikiriza nga bwe balaamiragana okusaasiragana
  90,18,Abo nno beebo abokubeera ku mukono ogwa ddyo
  90,19,Naye abo abawakanya e bigambo byaffe baakubeera ku mukono ogwa kkono
  90,20,Bagenda kubeera mu muliro omusaanikire
  91,1,Ndayira e njuba n’okwaka kwayo
  91,2,Era ndayira o mwezi bweguba nga gugoberedde e njuba (ng’egudde)
  91,3,Era ndayira obudde obw’emisana nga bwerudde enjuba
  91,4,Era ndayira ekiro bwe kiba nga kigibisse
  91,5,Era ndayira e ggulu n’eyalitonda
  91,6,Era ndayira e nsi n’oyo eyajaaliira
  91,7,Era ndayira omuntu n’eyamutonda
  91,8,N’amuwa okwawula wakati w’ekibi n’ekirungi
  91,9,Yeesiimye alongoosa omwoyogwe okuguggya mu bibi
  91,10,Aviiriddemu awo oyo agunnyika mu bibi
  91,11,"Abantu ba Thamuud, olw'obwonoonefu bwabwe baalimbisa (omubaka waabwe)"
  91,12,Asinga obwonoonefu mu bo bwe yeesowolayo (naafumita engamiya)
  91,13,Omubaka wa Katonda n’abagamba “muleke e ngamiya ya Katonda n’okunywa kwayo”
  91,14,Kyokka ne bamulimbisa ne bagifumita. Katonda omulabirizi waabwe kwe kubabuutikira olw’obwonoonefu bwabwe awatali n’omu kuwona
  91,15,Era tatya nkomerero y'ekyo (eky'okubazikiriza)
  92,1,Ndayira ekiro bwe kiba kibisse (e nsi)
  92,2,Ndayira n'obudde bwemisana bwe buba nga bwetadde
  92,3,Ndayira oyo eyatonda ekisajja n’ekikazi
  92,4,Mazima ddala okulafuubana kwa mmwe si kwe kumu
  92,5,"N'olwekyo, omuntu awaayo ekintu kyonna ng’atya Katonda"
  92,6,Nakkiriza e birungi. (ebiva mu kukkiriza Katonda)
  92,7,Tujja kumwanguyiza e kkubo erimutuusa eri obwangu
  92,8,Ate oyo akodowala ne yeegaggasa (ng’alowooza nti ebiri ewa Katonda tabyetaaga)
  92,9,N’alimbisa obubaka obwakkira ku Nabbi Muhammad
  92,10,Tujja kumwanguyiza okutuuka eri obuzibu
  92,11,N’obugaggabwe tebugenda kumugasa ng’ayingidde okuzikirira (olw’ebikolwa bye ebibi)
  92,12,Mazima kuli ku ffe okulungamya
  92,13,Era mazima ebikwata ku nkomerero ne nsi biri mu buyinza bwaffe
  92,14,Mbeekesa omuliro ogubumbujja
  92,15,Taliguyingira okugyako oyo omwonoonefu ennyo
  92,16,Oyo alimbisa (e bigambo bya Katonda) n'ayawukana (ku kugondera n'okukkiriza Katonda)
  92,17,"So nga oyo asinga okutya Katonda, ajja kugwesambisibwa"
  92,18,Oyo awaayo ku by'alina ng’anoonya okwetukuza eri Katonda (so si bandabe oba okwatiikirira)
  92,19,Nga tewali n'omu alina kiyinza ku musasulwa
  92,20,Wabula okunoonya okusiimwa ewa mukamaawe owa waggulu ennyo
  92,21,Mazima ddala ajja kusiima (ky’anaasasulwa)
  93,1,Ndayira ekiseera ky’a kalasa mayanzi
  93,2,Era ndayira e kiro bwekiba nga kikutte
  93,3,Omuleziwo Katonda takwabuliranga (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) era takukyawanga
  93,4,Era ddala e nkomerero y’ennungi gy’oli okusinga entandikwa
  93,5,Era ddala Omuleziwo ajja kukuwa naawe osiime
  93,6,Teyakusanga ng’oli mulekwa n'akulabirira
  93,7,Era teyakusanga nga tomanyi n’akulungamya
  93,8,Era teyakusanga nga oli mwavu n’akugaggawaza
  93,9,Kale nno mulekwa tomukaayuukiranga
  93,10,N’omuntu asaba tomuboggoleranga
  93,11,Ate era e kyengera kyonna Omuleziwo Katonda ky’abanga akuwadde kinyumyengako
  94,1,Tetwakwanjululiza ekifubakyo (eri obwa Nabbi n’okumanya ebigambo eby’amagezi)
  94,2,Ne tukuwewulira obuzito obwakuliko
  94,3,Obuzito obwo obwalibadde bukubendula omugongo
  94,4,Era ne tukuwa okwogerwako
  94,5,"(Kisaana kitegerekeke nti) mazima ddala buli awabeera obuzibu, wabaawo obwangu"
  94,6,Mazima ddala buli awabeera obuzibu wabaawo obwangu
  94,7,Bwoba nga omaze okukola emirimu (egikuyimirizaawo ku nsi) olwo nno yimirira (osinze Katondawo)
  94,8,"Era eri Omuleziwo Katonda, gy’oba oteeka e ssuubilyo lyonna"
  95,1,Ndayira ekibala ekiyitibwa Tiin n’ekibala ekiyitibwa Zaitun
  95,2,Era ndayira olusozi lw’e Sinai
  95,3,Nakino e kibuga (Makkah) eky’emirembe
  95,4,Mazima twakola omuntu mu kifaananyi e kisinga okuba ekirungi
  95,5,Ate oluvanyuma tumuzzaayo wansi mu ddaala erisembayo
  95,6,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi, bagenda kufuna e mpeera etalina kkomo"
  95,7,Bwekiba bw'ekityo (ate gwe omuntu) olimbisa otya olunaku lw'enkomerero
  95,8,Tolaba nti Katonda ye Mulamuzi asinga okuba omwenkanya era owamazima
  96,1,Soma ng'otandika ne linnya lya mukamawo oyo eyatonda (buli kintu)
  96,2,Yatonda omuntu nga amuggya mu kisaayisaayi
  96,3,"Soma, kuba Omulezi wo (Katonda) ye mugabi asinga"
  96,4,Oyo eyayigiriza omuntu okuwandiika n'ekkalaamu
  96,5,Yayigiriza omuntu ebyo (omuntu) bye yali tamanyi
  96,6,"Nedda, mazima omuntu agenda neyewaggula"
  96,7,Olw’okweraba nti yeemalirira (olw’ebyo by’aba alina)
  96,8,Ng’ate Mazima ddala eri Omuleziwo (Katonda) y’eri obuddo
  96,9,Olabye omuntu agaana
  96,10,(Agaana) omuddu wa Katonda bw’aba ng'asaala
  96,11,Tolaba nti gwebagaana ky'akola kya bulungamu
  96,12,Oba bwaba alagidde abantu okutya Katonda
  96,13,Olaba oyo (agaana asaala) bw'alimbisa n'akyuka okuva ku mazima
  96,14,Abaffe tamanyi (oyo alimbisa) nti Mazima Katonda alaba ebyo (by’akola)
  96,15,Nedda bw’anaaba teyeekomyeko (ku bikolwa ebyo) tujja kumuwalula nga tumukutte ku kawompo
  96,16,Akawompo ako akajjudde obulimba n’obusobya
  96,17,Kale ayitanga abali mu kinywi kye (eky’obujeemu bamutaase)
  96,18,Naffe tujja kukoowoola ba Malayika abakambwe abakuumi b’omuliro (abatuusa ebibonerezo ku bajeemu)
  96,19,Nedda (Owange Nabbi Muhammad) togonderanga omuntu ng’oyo. Vunnama (ng'osinza) Katonda era weeyongere okusembera gy'ali
  97,1,Mazima ffe twassa Kur'ani mu kiro ekiyitibwa Layila-tul-kadri (e kiro ekyokugera era ekyekitiibwa)
  97,2,Ye nno omanyi Layila-tul-kadri kye ki
  97,3,Layila-tul-kadri kiro kirungi okusinga emyezi olukumi
  97,4,"Mu kiro ekyo, ba Mlayika bakka nga ne Jiburilu mwali ku lw’ekiragiro kya mukama waabwe (Katonda). Nga bajja na buli kiragiro"
  97,5,"Ekiro ekyo kya mirembe myereere, okutuusa obudde okukya"
  98,1,"Abajeemu mu bantu abaweebwa e kitabo, n'abo abagatta ebintu ebirala ku Katonda, tebaali baakuva ku nzikiriza yaabwe enkyamu okutuusa nga obunnyonnyofu bubajjidde"
  98,2,"Nga, ye Mubaka (Nabbi Muhammad) eyatumwa okuva ewa Katonda, nga asoma ekitabo ekitukuvu (Kur'ani)"
  98,3,Ekirimu amateeka amalambulukufu
  98,4,Era abantu abo abaweebwa e kitabo tebayawukanayawukana okutuusa nga obunnyonnyofu bumaze okubajjira
  98,5,"So nga ate tebaalagirwa okugyako okusinza Katonda yekka nga buli kyebakola bakikola ku lulwe yekka, awatali ku mugattirizaako kantu konna. Era nga bateekwa okuyimirizaawo e sswala n’okutoola Zzaka. Era nga eyo nno y'eddiini ennambulukufu"
  98,6,Mazima abo abaajeema mu bantu abaaweebwa e kitabo n’abo abagatta ku Katonda e bintu ebirala bakuyingira omuliro Jahannama mwe bagenda okubeera olubeerera. Abo nno be babi okusinga ebitonde ebirala byonna
  98,7,Mazima abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi be balungi okusinga ebitonde byonna
  98,8,"E mpeera yaabwe ewa Katonda waabwe kubayingiza jjana eyitibwa Aden, nga emigga gikulukutira mu yo. Baakugibeeramu olubeerera. Katonda yabasiima nabo ne bamusiima. Ebyo nno bigenda kufunwa oyo eyatya omuleziwe (Katonda)"
  99,1,E nsi bweriba eyuguumizziddwa oluyuguuma lwayo
  99,2,E nsi n'efulumya (nga ewandula) ebyo byonna ebigirimu
  99,3,Omuntu aligamba nga yeebuuza nti! ebadde ki
  99,4,Ku lunaku olwo egenda kuttottola ebigambo byonna ebikwata ku ebyo ebyakolerwanga ku yo
  99,5,Nti mazima Katonda y'aliba agiragidde okwogera ebyo
  99,6,Abantu ku lunaku olwo baliva mu kabbuli zaabwe nga bali mu bibinja babe nga balagibwa e mirimu gyabwe
  99,7,Omuntu eyakola omulimu omulungi gwonna kagube mutono gutya agenda kugulaba
  99,8,N'omuntu eyakola omulimu omubi gwonna kagube mutono gutya agenda kugulaba
  100,1,Ndayira embalaasi ezizinda(ezidduka) nga ziweevuuma
  100,2,Nezimansula e nsasi z’omuliroolw’okukoona enjazi
  100,3,Ezizinda ku maliiri
  100,4,"Nezisiikuula enfuufu, mu kutyekuula emisinde okwo"
  100,5,Neziyingira mu balabe wakati
  100,6,Mazima ddala omuntu mutomi eri omuleziwe
  100,7,Era mazima ye (omuntu) ku ky'obutomi mujulizi
  100,8,Era mazima yye muyitirivu nnyo mu kwagala ebyenfuna
  100,9,Abaffe (omuntu) tamanyi nti ebiri mu kabbuli bwe biriba bizuukiziddwa
  100,10,N’ebiri mu bifuba ne byolesebwa
  100,11,Mazima Katonda omulezi waabwe (nga bulijjo ne) ku lunaku olwo agenda kuba ng'amanyi byonna ebibakwatako
  101,1,Ekikoona (ekyentiisa)
  101,2,Ekikoona kye ki
  101,3,Naye omanyi ekikoona kye ki
  101,4,Lwe lunaku abantu lwe balibeera nga e biwojjolo ebisaasaanye
  101,5,N’ensozi lwe zirifuuka nga pamba omusuunsule afuumuuka
  101,6,"Naye, omuntu alibeera n'emirimu e mirungi nga gizitowa (okusinga ebibibye)"
  101,7,Oyo agenda kubeera mu bulamu obw’okwesiima
  101,8,Ate oyo aliwewukirwa emirimu gye emirungi (ebibi bye n’ebisinga obuzito)
  101,9,"Oyo nno, obuddo n'obutuulo bwe muliro oguyitibwa “Haawiya”"
  101,10,Naye omanyi ‘Haawiya’ kye ki
  101,11,Gwe muliro ogwengeredde (ogwokya ennyo)
  102,1,"Okunoonya okufuna ebingi, kubalabankanyizza (ne kubajja ku kugondera amateeka ga Katonda)"
  102,2,Okutuusa lwe muyingira kabbuli
  102,3,"Nedda, kyaddaki mujja kumanya (mu kiseera ky'okufa)"
  102,4,"Ate era oluvanyuma, kyaddaki mujja kumanya (nga muyingidde kabbuli)"
  102,5,"Nedda, singa nga mubadde mumanyi mu bukakafu bw'okumanya (temwandirabankanyiziddwa na kukungaanya bingi)"
  102,6,Mujja kulabira ddala omuliro “Jahiim”
  102,7,Ate oluvanyuma omuliro ogwo mujja kugulaba mugutegeerere ddala
  102,8,"Ate ddala oluvanyuma mugenda kubuuzibwa e byengera bye mwafuna ku nsi (mwabifuna mu makubo ki, era mwabisaasaanya mu makubo ki)"
  103,1,Ndayira omulembe (buli mulembe)
  103,2,Mazima ddala omuntu yenna gy’afa yenkana ali mu kufaafaaganirwa
  103,3,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza Katonda (mu nzikiriza entuufu) ate ne bakola e mirimu emirungi, era ne balaamirigana okukoleranga ku mazima (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna) era ne balaamiragana okubeera abagumikiriza (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna)"
  104,1,"Okubonaabona okwamaanyi kugenda kubeera ku buli muntu atambuza engambo, ageya banne n'abaggya obumogo"
  104,2,Oyo akungaanya ebyo bugagga n’abituuma
  104,3,Alowooza nti eby'obugaggabye byakumukuumira ku nsi obugenderevu
  104,4,"Nedda, ajja kukanyugwa mu muliro oguyitibwa “Hutwama”"
  104,5,Ye omanyi “Hutwama” kye ki
  104,6,"(Hutwama) muliro gwa Katonda omukume, ogubumbujja"
  104,7,Ogwo ogwokya negutuukira ddala ku mitima
  104,8,Mazima ddala omuliro ogwo (Hutwama) ku bantu abo (abogeddwaako) gugenda kubabuutikira
  104,9,Mu midumu emiwanvu
  105,1,Tewamanya Katonda kyeyakola eggye ly’enjovu
  105,2,Enkwe zaabwe tezaagwa butaka
  105,3,N'abasindikira e binnyonyi nga bijjira mu bibinja
  105,4,Nga bibakanyugira amayinja amookye
  105,5,Nebafuuka nga omuddo ogagayiddwa ensolo ne gufuluma nga gufuuse obusa
  106,1,Ku lw'empangaala ya ba Kuraish
  106,2,Empangaala yaabwe eyalimu okutambula engendo mu butiti ne mu kyeya
  106,3,Bateekwa basinze Katonda nannyini nyumba eno (Kaaba)
  106,4,"Katonda eyabawa eby'okulya, n’abawonya enjala, n’abawa e mirembe, ne bataba mu kutya"
  107,1,Olabye oyo alimbisa olunaku lw'enkomerero
  107,2,Oyo nno y’oyo awalagganya ba mulekwa
  107,3,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  107,4,Okubonaabona kuli ku abo abasaala
  107,5,Nga balagajjalira e sswala zaabwe
  107,6,Abo abakola bandabe
  107,7,Era abamma bannaabwe ebintu ebitasaana kumma
  108,1,"Mazima ffe twakuwa e birungi e bingi, (mu ebyo mwe muli n'oluzzi Kauthara olw'omu jjana)"
  108,2,"N'olwekyo wenywereze ku kusaala ku lwa Katondawo, era osale n’ebisolo, nga osaddaaka ku lwa Katondawo"
  108,3,"Mazima oyo akuwalagganya, (ng'akuvuma era n'okukujeeja) ye wenkuggu"
  109,1,"Bagambe nti, abange mmwe abatakkiriza (abawakanyi)"
  109,2,"Ssisinza ebyo bye musinza (amasanamu, lubaale, n'ebirala)"
  109,3,Wadde namwe temusinza oyo gwe nsinza (ali omu mu bwa Katonda bwe)
  109,4,Era siri waakusinza ebyo bye musinza
  109,5,Era nammwe temuli baakusinza oyo gwensinza
  109,6,"Mulina e nkola yammwe (ey'okusinza ba Katonda abangi, nange nnina enkola yange (ey'okusinza Katonda omu yekka)"
  110,1,Okutaasa kwa Katonda n’obuwanguzi bwe bijjanga
  110,2,N’olaba abantu nga bayingira e ddiini ya Katonda mu bibinja
  110,3,"Otenderezanga Mukama Katondawo n’ebitendobye, era omwetondere, mazima yye akkiriza okwenenya"
  111,1,"Mu Hadith eri mu kitabo kya Bukhari Nabbi yagenda ku Batwhahu naakuba wuuli abantu bangi bajja nga balowooza nti waliyo ebya maguzi, Nabbi bweyatandika okubabuulira ebikwata ku Katonda, Abu Lahbi naakasuka e mikono nga bwagamba nti kino kyotukunganyirizza era kyotuyitidde? Zikirira. Katonda kwe kumwanukula mu ssura eno naagamba nti: (Gizikirire e mikono gya Abu Lahbi (gyawuuba), era ddala yenna yazikirira"
  111,2,"Eby'obugaggabwe tebimugasizza, wadde n’ebirala bye yafuna, (nga e kitiibwa)"
  111,3,Ajja kwesonseka mu muliro ogubumbujja
  111,4,Ne mukyalawe omwetissi w’enku (naye bwatyo)
  111,5,Nga mu nsingoye mulimu omuguwa omulange
  112,1,(Gwe Nabbi Muhammad) bagambe nti Katonda ali omu mu bwa Katondabwe (era nga yye yekka ateekeddwa okusinzibwa)
  112,2,Katonda y'akola ku byetaago by'ebitonde byonna
  112,3,"Tazaala, era teyazaalibwa"
  112,4,Era teri kintu kyonna kimwenkana
  113,1,"Gamba nti, nsaba obukuumi ewa Katonda afuga okukya kw’obudde"
  113,2,Mu bubi bw’ebyo bye yatonda
  113,3,Ne mu bubi bw’ekiro nga kikutte
  113,4,Ne mu bubi bw’abakazi abalogo abasiba ebifundikwa (ne babifuuwamu nga balaamiriza)
  113,5,Ne mu bubi obuva mu mukozi wensaalwa ng'akoze ensaalwa
  114,1,"Gamba nti, nsaba obukuumi okuva eri Mukama omulabirizi wa bantu"
  114,2,Omufuzi w'abantu
  114,3,Asinzibwa abantu
  114,4,Amponye obubi bw’omulabankanya sitaani omwekwesi
  114,5,Oyo alabankanya (e mitima egiri) mu bifuba by'abantu
  114,6,(Sitaani) ow’omu majiinni ne sitaani ow’omu bantu